<document xmlns="http://cnx.rice.edu/cnxml" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
<title>Útfelling og upplausn</title>
<metadata xmlns:md="http://cnx.rice.edu/mdml">
  <md:content-id>m68811</md:content-id>
  <md:title>Útfelling og upplausn</md:title>
  <md:abstract><para id="para-00001">Í lok þessa kafla muntu geta:</para><list id="list-00001"><item>Skrifað efnajöfnur og jafnvægislíkingar sem tákna leysnijafnvægi</item><item>Framkvæmt jafnvægisútreikninga sem fela í sér leysni, jafnvægislíkingar og styrk leystra efna</item></list></md:abstract>
  <md:uuid>12ccafb5-1b00-4ffd-81c3-dfc8b9fa2959</md:uuid>
</metadata>

<content>
<para id="fs-idp15457056">Leysnijafnvægi komast á þegar upplausn og útfelling leystrar efnisagna eiga sér stað á sama hraða. Þessi jafnvægi liggja til grundvallar mörgum náttúrulegum og tæknilegum ferlum, allt frá tannskemmdum til vatnshreinsunar. Skilningur á þeim þáttum sem hafa áhrif á leysni efnasambanda er því nauðsynlegur fyrir skilvirka stjórnun þessara ferla. Í þessum kafla er beitt áður kynntum jafnvægisreglum og verkfærum á kerfi sem fela í sér upplausn og útfellingu.</para>
<section id="fs-idp15827408">
<title>Leysnimargfeldið</title>
<para id="fs-idm402040992">Rifjum upp úr kaflanum um lausnir að leysni efnis getur verið allt frá nánast engri (<emphasis effect="italics">óleysanlegt</emphasis> eða <emphasis effect="italics">torleyst</emphasis>) upp í óendanlega (<emphasis effect="italics">samblandanlegt</emphasis>). Leyst efni með takmarkaða leysni getur myndað <emphasis effect="italics">mettaða</emphasis> lausn þegar því er bætt í leysi í magni sem er meira en leysni þess, sem leiðir til misleitrar efnablöndu af mettuðu lausninni og umframmagni af óuppleystu leysið efni. Til dæmis er mettuð lausn af silfurklóríði lausn þar sem jafnvægið sem sýnt er hér að neðan hefur komist á.</para>
<equation id="fs-idp15836912" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>AgCl</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:munderover><m:mo>⇌</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mtext>precipitation</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mtext>dissolution</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:munderover><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ag</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Cl</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp292944">Í þessari lausn leysist umframmagn af föstu AgCl upp og sundrast og myndar Ag<sup>+</sup> og Cl<sup>–</sup> jónir í vatnslausn á sama hraða og þessar vatnsjónir sameinast og falla út og mynda fast AgCl (<link target-id="CNX_Chem_15_01_AgCl"/>). Vegna þess að silfurklóríð er torleyst salt er jafnvægisstyrkur uppleystra jóna þess í lausninni tiltölulega lágur.</para>
<figure id="CNX_Chem_15_01_AgCl">
<media id="fs-idp15452416" alt="Two beakers are shown with a bidirectional arrow between them. Both beakers are just over half filled with a clear, colorless liquid. The beaker on the left shows a cubic structure composed of alternating green and slightly larger grey spheres. Evenly distributed in the region outside, 11 space filling models are shown. These are each composed of a central red sphere with two smaller white spheres attached in a bent arrangement. In the beaker on the right, the green and grey spheres are no longer connected in a cubic structure. Nine green spheres, 10 grey spheres, and 11 red and white molecules are evenly mixed and distributed throughout the liquid in the beaker.">
<image mime-type="image/jpeg" class="scaled-down" src="../../media/CNX_Chem_15_01_AgCl.jpg"/>
</media>
<caption>Silfurklóríð er torleyst jónaefni í föstu formi. Þegar því er bætt í vatn leysist það örlítið upp og myndar efnablöndu sem samanstendur af mjög þunnri lausn af Ag<sup>+</sup> og Cl<sup>–</sup> jónum í jafnvægi við óuppleyst silfurklóríð.</caption>
</figure>
<para id="fs-idp15439888">Jafnvægisfastinn fyrir leysnijafnvægi eins og þetta er kallaður <emphasis effect="bold">leysnimargfeldisfasti, <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub></emphasis>, í þessu tilfelli</para>
<equation id="fs-idp15217968" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>AgCl</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ag</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Cl</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="4em"/><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ag</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mtext>Cl</m:mtext><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp15825056">Rifjum upp að aðeins lofttegundir og leyst efni eru táknuð í jafnvægisfastalíkingum, þannig að <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> inniheldur ekki lið fyrir óuppleysta AgCl. Listi yfir leysnimargfeldisfasta fyrir nokkur torleyst efnasambönd er að finna í <link document="m68868">Appendix J</link>.</para>
<example id="fs-idm38560">
<para id="fs-idm38304"><title>Að skrifa jöfnur og leysnimargfeldi</title>Skrifaðu upplausnarjöfnuna og leysnimargfeldislíkinguna fyrir hvert af eftirfarandi örlítið leysanlegu jónaefnasamböndum:</para>
<para id="fs-idp204000">(a) AgI, silfurjoðíð, fast efni með sótthreinsandi eiginleika</para>
<para id="fs-idp15889200">(b) CaCO<sub>3</sub>, kalsíumkarbónat, virka innihaldsefnið í mörgum sýrubindandi tuggutöflum sem fást án lyfseðils</para>
<para id="fs-idp681040">(c) Mg(OH)<sub>2</sub>, magnesíumhýdroxíð, virka innihaldsefnið í Milk of Magnesia</para>
<para id="fs-idp11820496">(d) Mg(NH<sub>4</sub>)PO<sub>4</sub>, magnesíumammóníumfosfat, nánast óleysanlegt efni sem notað er í prófunum fyrir magnesíum</para>
<para id="fs-idp291040">(e) Ca<sub>5</sub>(PO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>3</sub>OH, steinefnið apatít, uppspretta fosfats fyrir áburð</para>
<para id="fs-idp313008"><title>Lausn</title><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtable><m:mtr><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mtext>a</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mtext>AgI</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ag</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mtext>I</m:mtext><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd/><m:mtd columnalign="right"><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo>=</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mtext>Ag</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mtext>I</m:mtext><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mtext>b</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CaCO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ca</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd/><m:mtd columnalign="right"><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo>=</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ca</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo>]</m:mo><m:mo>[</m:mo><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mtext>c</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Mg</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Mg</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>2OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd/><m:mtd columnalign="right"><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo>=</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Mg</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mtext>d</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mtext>Mg</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>4</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>PO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>4</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Mg</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>PO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>3−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd/><m:mtd columnalign="right"><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo>=</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Mg</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mtext>NH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mtext>PO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>3−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mtext>e</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ca</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>PO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>5Ca</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>3PO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>3−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd/><m:mtd columnalign="right"><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo>=</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:msup><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mtext>Ca</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mtext>P</m:mtext><m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>3−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mtd></m:mtr></m:mtable></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp413568"><title>Kannaðu þekkingu þína</title>Skrifaðu upplausnarjöfnuna og leysnimargfeldið fyrir hvert af eftirfarandi örlítið leysanlegu efnasamböndum:</para>
<para id="fs-idp414352">(a) BaSO<sub>4</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idp414992">(b) Ag<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>4</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idp11828480">(c) Al(OH)<sub>3</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idp11829120">(d) Pb(OH)Cl</para>
<note id="fs-idp11829504"><title>Answer:</title><para id="fs-idp11829888"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtable><m:mtr><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mtext>a</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>BaSO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ba</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>SO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd/><m:mtd columnalign="right"><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo>=</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mtext>Ba</m:mtext><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mtext>SO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>;</m:mo></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mtext>b</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ag</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>SO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>2Ag</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>SO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd/><m:mtd columnalign="right"><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo>=</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ag</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>SO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>;</m:mo></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mtext>c</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Al</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Al</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>3+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>3OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd/><m:mtd columnalign="right"><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo>=</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Al</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>3+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mtext>3</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>;</m:mo></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mtext>d</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mtext>Pb(OH)Cl(</m:mtext><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Pb</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Cl</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd/><m:mtd columnalign="right"><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo>=</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Pb</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Cl</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mtd></m:mtr></m:mtable></m:mrow></m:math></para></note>
</example>
</section>
<section id="fs-idp11911328">
<title><emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> og leysni</title>
<para id="fs-idp11912720"><emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> örlítið leysanlegs jónaefnasambands má einfaldlega tengja við mælda leysni þess að því gefnu að upplausnarferlið feli aðeins í sér sundrun og leysingu, til dæmis:</para>
<equation id="fs-idp11914144" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext>M</m:mtext><m:mi>p</m:mi></m:msub><m:msub><m:mtext>X</m:mtext><m:mi>q</m:mi></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:mi>p</m:mi><m:msup><m:mtext>M</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mtext>m+</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:msup><m:mtext>X</m:mtext><m:mtext>n−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp843744">Í tilfellum sem þessum er hægt að leiða út <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> gildi úr uppgefinni leysni, eða öfugt. Útreikningar af þessu tagi eru best framkvæmdir með því að nota mólstyrksleysni efnasambands, mælt sem mól af uppleystu leysið efni á hvern lítra af mettaðri lausn.</para>
<example id="fs-idp844816">
<para id="fs-idp845072"><title>Útreikningur á <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> út frá jafnvægisstyrk</title>Flúorít, CaF<sub>2</sub>, er örlítið leysanlegt fast efni sem leysist upp samkvæmt jöfnunni:</para>
<equation id="fs-idp847472" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CaF</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ca</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>2F</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp15201792">Styrkur Ca<sup>2+</sup> í mettaðri lausn af CaF<sub>2</sub> er 2,15 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–4</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>. Hvert er leysnimargfeldi flúoríts?</para><para id="fs-idp15206752"><title>Lausn</title>Samkvæmt hlutfallaefnafræði upplausnarjöfnunnar er mólstyrkur flúoríðjóna í CaF<sub>2</sub> lausn jafn tvöföldum mólstyrk kalsíumjóna:</para>
<equation id="fs-idm421605264" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo> <m:mrow><m:msup><m:mtext>F</m:mtext><m:mo>−</m:mo></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mtext>mol</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mtext>F</m:mtext><m:mo>−</m:mo></m:msup><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mtext>/</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mtext>mol</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ca</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>2.15</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4.30</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idm332364112">Með því að setja styrk jónanna inn í <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> jöfnuna fæst</para>
<equation id="fs-idm55552" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ca</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mtext>F</m:mtext><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>(2.15</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mn>4.30</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>3.98</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>11</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp16640"><title>Kannaðu þekkingu þína</title>Í mettaðri lausn af Mg(OH)<sub>2</sub> er styrkur Mg<sup>2+</sup> 1,31 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–4</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>. Hvert er leysnimargfeldið fyrir Mg(OH)<sub>2</sub>?</para><equation id="fs-idp19952" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Mg(OH)</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Mg</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>2OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<note id="fs-idp259840"><title>Answer:</title><para id="fs-idp260224">8,99 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–12</sup></para></note>
</example>
<example id="fs-idp261504">
<para id="fs-idp261760"><title>Ákvörðun mólarleysni út frá <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub></title><emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> kopar(I)brómíðs, CuBr, er 6,3 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–9</sup>. Reiknaðu mólarleysni koparbrómíðs.</para>
<para id="fs-idp264928"><title>Lausn</title>Upplausnarjafnan og jafna leysnimargfeldisins eru</para>
<equation id="fs-idp266848" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>CuBr</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Cu</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Br</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<equation id="fs-idp590896" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Cu</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Br</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp594736">Með því að fylgja ICE-aðferðinni við þennan útreikning fæst taflan</para>
<media id="fs-idp596176" class="scaled-down" alt="This table has two main columns and four rows. The first row for the first column does not have a heading and then has the following in the first column: Initial concentration ( M ), Change ( M ), and Equilibrium concentration ( M ). The second column has the header of, “C u B r equilibrium arrow C u superscript positive sign plus B r superscript negative sign.” Under the second column is a subgroup of three rows and three columns. The first column is blank. The second column has the following: 0, positive x, x. The third column has the following 0, positive x, x.">
<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_Chem_15_01_ICETable1_img.jpg"/>
</media>
<para id="fs-idp597536">Með því að setja liðina fyrir jafnvægisstyrk inn í jöfnu leysnimargfeldisins og leysa fyrir <emphasis effect="italics">x</emphasis> fæst</para>
<equation id="fs-idp597920" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo>[</m:mo><m:mtext>Cu</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Br</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<equation id="fs-idp602000" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>6.3</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msup><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<equation id="fs-idp15508368" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mn>6.3</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>7.9</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp15515696">Þar sem hlutfallaefnafræði upplausnarinnar sýnir að eitt mól af kopar(I)jón og eitt mól af brómíðjón myndast fyrir hvert mól af Br sem leysist upp, er mólarleysni CuBr 7,9 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–5</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>.</para>
<para id="fs-idp15517600"><title>Kannaðu þekkingu þína</title><emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> AgI er 1,5 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–16</sup>. Reiknaðu mólarleysni silfurjoðíðs.</para>
<note id="fs-idp645648"><title>Answer:</title><para id="fs-idp646032">1,2 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–8</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para></note>
</example>
<example id="fs-idp647936">
<para id="fs-idp648192"><title>Ákvörðun mólarleysni út frá <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub></title><emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> kalsíumhýdroxíðs, Ca(OH)<sub>2</sub>, er 1,3 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–6</sup>. Reiknaðu mólarleysni kalsíumhýdroxíðs.</para><para id="fs-idp651872"><title>Lausn</title>Upplausnarjafnan og jafna leysnimargfeldisins eru</para>
<equation id="fs-idp653824" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ca(OH)</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ca</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>2OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<equation id="fs-idp662160" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ca</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp15421424">ICE-taflan fyrir þetta kerfi er</para>
<media id="fs-idp15423072" class="scaled-down" alt="This table has two main columns and four rows. The first row for the first column does not have a heading and then has the following in the first column: Initial concentration ( M ), Change ( M ), and Equilibrium concentration ( M ). The second column has the header of, “C a ( O H ) subscript 2 equilibrium arrow C a superscript 2 positive sign plus 2 O H superscript negative sign.” Under the second column is a subgroup of three rows and three columns. The first column is blank. The second column has the following: 0, positive x, x. The third column has the following 0, positive 2 x, 2 x.">
<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_Chem_15_01_ICETable7_img.jpg"/>
</media>
<para id="fs-idp15424432">Með því að setja liði fyrir jafnvægisstyrk inn í jöfnu leysnimargfeldisins og leysa fyrir <emphasis effect="italics">x</emphasis> fæst</para>
<equation id="fs-idp15424816" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ca</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<equation id="fs-idp15429408" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1.3</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mtext>​</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:msup><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:msup><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation><equation id="fs-idp820144" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mroot><m:mrow><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>1.3</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mroot><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>6.9</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math></equation><para id="fs-idp827984">Eins og skilgreint er í ICE-töflunni er <emphasis effect="italics">x</emphasis> mólstyrkur kalsíumjóna í mettuðu lausninni. Hlutfallaefnafræði upplausnarinnar sýnir 1:1 samband milli móla kalsíumjóna í lausn og móla af uppleystu efnasambandi, og því er mólarleysni Ca(OH)<sub>2</sub> 6,9 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>.</para><para id="fs-idp830272"><title>Kannaðu þekkingu þína</title><emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> PbI<sub>2</sub> er 1,4 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–8</sup>. Reiknaðu mólarleysni blý(II)joðíðs.</para>
<note id="fs-idp833104"><title>Answer:</title><para id="fs-idp833488">1,5 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para></note>
</example>
<example id="fs-idp836192">
<para id="fs-idp836448"><title>Ákvörðun <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> út frá leysni í grömmum</title>Mörg litarefnanna sem listamenn nota í olíumálningu (<link target-id="CNX_Chem_15_01_OilPaints"/>) eru torleyst í vatni. Til dæmis er leysni litarefnisins króm-guls, PbCrO<sub>4</sub>, 4,6 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–6</sup> g/L. Ákvarðaðu leysnimargfeldið fyrir PbCrO<sub>4</sub>.</para><!-- figure handled separately -->
<para id="fs-idp612896"><title>Lausn</title></para>
<para id="fs-idp619872">Áður en leysnimargfeldið er reiknað verður að breyta uppgefnum leysni í mólstyrk:</para>
<equation id="fs-idp120984032" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mtable><m:mtr/><m:mtr/><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mo>[</m:mo> <m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>PbCrO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub></m:mrow> <m:mo>]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>4.6</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>g PbCrO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mtext>L</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.4em"/><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mspace width="0.4em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mtext>mol PbCrO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>323.2</m:mn><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mtext>g PbCrO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>1.4</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mtext>mol PbCrO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mtext>L</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mn>1.4</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:mtd></m:mtr></m:mtable></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp15351552">Upplausnarjafnan fyrir þetta efnasamband er</para>
<equation id="fs-idp100842208" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>PbCrO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Pb</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CrO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp53410000">Hlutfallaefnafræði upplausnarinnar sýnir 1:1 samband milli mólmagns efnasambandsins og tveggja jóna þess, og því er bæði [Pb<sup>2+</sup>] og <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CrO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> jafnt mólarleysni PbCrO<sub>4</sub>:</para>
<equation id="fs-idp34481696" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Pb</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CrO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>1.4</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp83072"><emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> = [Pb<sup>2+</sup>]<m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CrO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> = (1,4 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–8</sup>)(1,4 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–8</sup>) = 2,0 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–16</sup></para>
<para id="fs-idp87280"><title>Kannaðu þekkingu þína</title>Leysni TlCl [þallín(I)klóríðs], milliefnis sem myndast þegar þallín er einangrað úr málmgrýti, er 3,12 grömm á lítra við 20 °C. Hvert er leysnimargfeldi þess?</para><note id="fs-idp88320"><title>Answer:</title><para id="fs-idp88704">1,69 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–4</sup></para></note>
</example>
<figure id="CNX_Chem_15_01_OilPaints" class="scaled-down">
<media id="fs-idp840928" alt="A photograph is shown of a portion of an oil painting which reveals colors of orange, brown, yellow, green, blue, and purple colors in its strokes. A few water droplets rest on the surface.">
<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_Chem_15_01_OilPaints.jpg"/>
</media>
<caption>Olíumálning inniheldur litarefni sem eru mjög lítið leysanleg í vatni. Auk króm-guls (PbCrO<sub>4</sub>) má nefna prússneskan bláan (Fe<sub>7</sub>(CN)<sub>18</sub>), rauðappelsínugula litinn vermilion (HgS) og græna litinn veridian (Cr<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub>). (Heimild: Sonny Abesamis)</caption>
</figure>
<example id="fs-idp91888">
<para id="fs-idp92144"><title>Útreikningur á leysni Hg<sub>2</sub>Cl<sub>2</sub></title>Kalómel, Hg<sub>2</sub>Cl<sub>2</sub>, er efnasamband sem samanstendur af tvíatóma jón kvikasilfurs(I), <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Hg</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>,</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>, og klóríðjónum, Cl<sup>–</sup>. Þótt flest kvikasilfurssambönd séu nú þekkt fyrir að vera eitruð, notuðu læknar á átjándu öld kalómel sem lyf. Sjúklingar þeirra urðu sjaldan fyrir kvikasilfurseitrun af meðferðunum vegna þess að kalómel hefur mjög lítinn leysni, eins og mjög lágt gildi <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> gefur til kynna:</para>
<equation id="fs-idp97168" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Hg</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Cl</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Hg</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>2Cl</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="4em"/><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>1.1</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp110192">Reiknaðu mólarleysni Hg<sub>2</sub>Cl<sub>2</sub>.</para>
<para id="fs-idp15521184"><title>Lausn</title>Hlutfallaefnafræði upplausnarinnar sýnir 1:1 samband milli magns uppleysts efnasambands og magns kvikasilfurs(I)jóna, og því er mólarleysni Hg<sub>2</sub>Cl<sub>2</sub> jafnt styrk <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Hg</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> jóna.</para>
<para id="fs-idm324614160">Að fylgja ICE-aðferðinni gefur:</para>
<media id="fs-idp15533712" class="scaled-down" alt="This table has two main columns and four rows. The first row for the first column does not have a heading and then has the following in the first column: Initial concentration ( M ), Change ( M ), Equilibrium concentration ( M ). The second column has the header of, “H g subscript 2 C l subscript 2 equilibrium arrow H g subscript 2 superscript 2 positive sign plus 2 C l superscript negative sign.” Under the second column is a subgroup of three rows and three columns. The first column is blank. The second column has the following: 0, positive x, x. The third column has the following: 0, positive 2 x, 2 x.">
<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_Chem_15_01_ICETable2_img.jpg"/>
</media>
<para id="fs-idm324611760">Með því að setja jafnvægisstyrksliðina inn í leysnimargfeldisjöfnuna og leysa fyrir <emphasis effect="italics">x</emphasis> fæst:</para>
<equation id="fs-idp53869216" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Hg</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2</m:mtext></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Cl</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<equation id="fs-idm14694048" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1.1</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<equation id="fs-idp127117360" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:msup><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>1.1</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<equation id="fs-idp29132112" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mroot><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>1.1</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mroot><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>6.5</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<equation id="fs-idp32484816" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Hg</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>6.5</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>6.5</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<equation id="fs-idm84487648" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Cl</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>2(6.5</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.3</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp15393408">Hlutfallaefnafræði upplausnarinnar sýnir að mólarleysni Hg<sub>2</sub>Cl<sub>2</sub> er jafnt og <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Hg</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2</m:mtext></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>,</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> eða 6,5 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–7</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>.</para>
<para id="fs-idp751088"><title>Kannaðu þekkingu þína</title>Ákvarðaðu mólarleysni MgF<sub>2</sub> út frá leysnimargfeldi þess: <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> = 6,4 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–9</sup>.</para>
<note id="fs-idp753920"><title>Answer:</title><para id="fs-idp754304">1,2 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para></note>
</example>
<note id="fs-idp765232" class="chemistry sciences-interconnect">
<title>Notkun baríumsúlfats við myndgreiningu í læknisfræði</title>
<para id="fs-idp766160">Ýmsar gerðir myndgreiningartækni eru notaðar til að aðstoða við sjúkdómsgreiningar á ífaralausan hátt. Ein slík tækni felur í sér inntöku baríumsambands áður en röntgenmynd er tekin. Sjúklingurinn innbyrðir grugglausn af baríumsúlfati, krítarkenndu dufti. Þar sem <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> baríumsúlfats er 10,08 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–10</sup>, leysist mjög lítið af því upp þegar það þekur slímhúð meltingarvegar sjúklingsins. Svæði meltingarvegarins sem eru þakin baríum birtast þá hvít á röntgenmynd, sem gerir kleift að sjá meiri smáatriði en á hefðbundinni röntgenmynd (<link target-id="CNX_Chem_15_01_BariumXray"/>).</para>
<figure id="CNX_Chem_15_01_BariumXray" class="scaled-down">
<media id="fs-idp770240" alt="This figure contains one image. A black and white abdominal x-ray image is shown in which the intestinal tract of a person is clearly visible in white.">
<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_Chem_15_01_BariumXray.jpg"/>
</media>
<caption>Grugglausn af baríumsúlfati þekur meltingarveginn og gerir kleift að sjá meiri smáatriði en á hefðbundinni röntgenmynd. (Heimild: breytt útgáfa af verki eftir „glitzy queen00“/Wikimedia Commons)</caption>
</figure>
<para id="fs-idp772848">Myndgreiningu með baríumsúlfati má nota til að greina bakflæðissjúkdóm, Crohns-sjúkdóm og magasár auk annarra sjúkdóma.</para>
<para id="fs-idp774080">Farðu á þessa <link url="http://openstax.org/l/16barium">website</link> vefsíðu til að fá frekari upplýsingar um hvernig baríum er notað við sjúkdómsgreiningar og hvaða sjúkdóma það er notað til að greina.</para>
</note>
</section>
<section id="fs-idp775600">
<title>Að spá fyrir um útfellingu</title>
<para id="fs-idp776288">Jafnan sem lýsir jafnvæginu milli fasts kalsíumkarbónats og uppleystra jóna þess er:</para>
<equation id="fs-idp776784" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtable><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CaCO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ca</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd/><m:mtd columnalign="right"><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mi>p</m:mi></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ca</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8.7</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mtd></m:mtr></m:mtable></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp785408">Mikilvægt er að gera sér grein fyrir því að þetta jafnvægi kemst á í hvaða vatnslausn sem er sem inniheldur Ca<sup>2+</sup> og CO<sub>3</sub><sup>2–</sup> jónir, ekki bara í lausn sem myndast við að metta vatn með kalsíumkarbónati. Íhugaðu til dæmis að blanda saman vatnslausnum af auðleystu efnasamböndunum natríumkarbónati og kalsíumnítrati. Ef styrkur kalsíum- og karbónatjóna í efnablöndunni gefur ekki hvarfstuðul, <emphasis effect="italics">Q<sub>sp</sub></emphasis>, sem er hærri en leysnimargfeldið, <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub>, þá verður engin útfelling. Ef styrkur jónanna gefur hvarfstuðul sem er hærri en leysnimargfeldið, þá verður útfelling sem lækkar þann styrk þar til jafnvægi er náð (<emphasis effect="italics">Q<sub>sp</sub></emphasis> = <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub>). Samanburður á <emphasis effect="italics">Q<sub>sp</sub></emphasis> og <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> til að spá fyrir um útfellingu er dæmi um almenna aðferð til að spá fyrir um stefnu efnahvarfs sem fyrst var kynnt í kaflanum um jafnvægi. Fyrir sértilfelli leysnijafnvægis gildir:</para>
<para id="fs-idm425158560"><emphasis effect="italics">Q<sub>sp</sub></emphasis> &lt; <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub>: efnahvarfið gengur í framátt (lausnin er ekki mettuð; engin útfelling sést)</para>
<para id="fs-idm425156768"><emphasis effect="italics">Q<sub>sp</sub></emphasis> > <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub>: efnahvarfið gengur í öfuga átt (lausnin er yfirmettuð; útfelling mun eiga sér stað)</para>
<para id="fs-idm425154976">Þessi forspáraðferð og tengdir útreikningar eru sýndir í næstu dæmum.</para>
<example id="fs-idp69099520">
<para id="fs-idp15157136"><title>Útfelling Mg(OH)<sub>2</sub></title>Fyrsta skrefið í framleiðslu á magnesíummálmi er útfelling Mg(OH)<sub>2</sub> úr sjó með álagningu á kalki, Ca(OH)<sub>2</sub>, sem er aðgengilegur og ódýr uppspretta OH<sup>–</sup> jóna:</para>
<equation id="fs-idp15159216" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Mg(OH)</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Mg</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>2OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="4em"/><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>8.9</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation><para id="fs-idp15170960">Styrkur Mg<sup>2+</sup>(<emphasis effect="italics">aq</emphasis>) í sjó er 0,0537 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>. Fellur Mg(OH)<sub>2</sub> út þegar nægu Ca(OH)<sub>2</sub> er bætt við til að gefa [OH<sup>–</sup>] upp á 0,0010 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>?</para>
<para id="fs-idp15174912"><title>Lausn</title></para>
<para id="fs-idp15183504">Útreikningur á hvarfstuðlinum við þessar aðstæður er sýndur hér:</para>
<equation id="fs-idp15187872" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>Q</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Mg</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>(0.0537)(</m:mtext><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>0.0010)</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>5.4</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp11854608">Þar sem <emphasis effect="italics">Q</emphasis> er stærra en <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> (<emphasis effect="italics">Q</emphasis> = 5,4 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–8</sup> er stærra en <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> = 8,9 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–12</sup>), mun öfuga efnahvarfið eiga sér stað og fella út magnesíumhýdroxíð þar til styrkur uppleystra jóna hefur lækkað nægilega, þannig að <emphasis effect="italics">Q<sub>sp</sub></emphasis> = <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub>.</para><para id="fs-idp11862608"><title>Kannaðu þekkingu þína</title>Spáðu fyrir um hvort CaHPO<sub>4</sub> muni falla út úr lausn með [Ca<sup>2+</sup>] = 0,0001 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> og <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HPO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> = 0,001 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>.</para>
<note id="fs-idp11869072"><title>Answer:</title><para id="fs-idp11869456">Engin útfelling á CaHPO<sub>4</sub>; <emphasis effect="italics">Q</emphasis> = 1 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–7</sup>, sem er minna en <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> (7 × 10<sup>–7</sup>)</para></note>
</example>
<example id="fs-idp11872704">
<para id="fs-idp11872960"><title>Útfelling AgCl</title>Fellur silfurklóríð út þegar jöfnu rúmmáli af 2,0 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–4</sup>-<emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> lausn af AgNO<sub>3</sub> og 2,0 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–4</sup>-<emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> lausn af NaCl er blandað saman?</para>
<para id="fs-idp11879728"><title>Lausn</title>Jafnan fyrir jafnvægið milli fasts silfurklóríðs, silfurjónar og klóríðjónar er:</para>
<equation id="fs-idp11880480" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>AgCl</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ag</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Cl</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp11887792">Leysnimargfeldið er 1,6 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–10</sup> (sjá <link document="m68868">Appendix J</link>).</para><para id="fs-idp11889984">AgCl mun falla út ef hvarfstuðullinn, reiknaður út frá styrknum í efnablöndu AgNO<sub>3</sub> og NaCl, er stærri en <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub>. Þar sem rúmmálið tvöfaldast þegar jöfnu rúmmáli af AgNO<sub>3</sub> og NaCl lausnum er blandað saman, minnkar hvor styrkur um helming frá upphafsgildi sínu.</para>
<equation id="fs-idp11893136" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mn>2.0</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>1.0</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp11902464">Hvarfstuðullinn, <emphasis effect="italics">Q</emphasis>, er stærri en <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> fyrir AgCl, þannig að yfirmettuð lausn myndast:</para>
<equation id="fs-idp456352" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>Q</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ag</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mtext>Cl</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>(1.0</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mn>1.0</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>1.0</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo>></m:mo><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp470144">AgCl mun falla út úr efnablöndunni þar til upplausnarjafnvægi er náð, þar sem <emphasis effect="italics">Q</emphasis> er jafnt og <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub>.</para>
<para id="fs-idp472176"><title>Kannaðu þekkingu þína</title>Fellur KClO<sub>4</sub> út þegar 20 ml af 0,050-<emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> lausn af K<sup>+</sup> er bætt við 80 ml af 0,50-<emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> lausn af <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>ClO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>?</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>? (Vísbending: Notið þynningarjöfnuna til að reikna út styrk kalíum- og perklóratjóna í efnablöndunni.)</para>
<note id="fs-idp477040"><title>Answer:</title><para id="fs-idp477424">Nei, <emphasis effect="italics">Q</emphasis> = 4,0 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–3</sup>, sem er minna en <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> = 1,05 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–2</sup></para></note>
</example>
<example id="fs-idp488672"><para id="fs-idp488928"><title>Útfelling kalsíumoxalats</title>Blóð storknar ekki ef kalsíumjónir eru fjarlægðar úr plasma þess. Sum blóðsöfnunarglös innihalda sölt oxalatjónarinnar, <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext>C</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>,</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>, í þessum tilgangi (<link target-id="CNX_Chem_15_01_Blood"/>). Við nægilega háan styrk mynda kalsíum- og oxalatjónir fast efni, CaC<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub>·H<sub>2</sub>O (kalsíumoxalat einhýdrat). Styrkur Ca<sup>2+</sup> í sýni úr blóðsermi er 2,2 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>. Hvaða styrk <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext>C</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> jónar þarf að ná áður en CaC<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub>·H<sub>2</sub>O byrjar að falla út?</para>
<!-- figure handled separately -->
<para id="fs-idp502656"><title>Lausn</title>Jafnvægislíkingin er:</para>
<equation id="fs-idp503344" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CaC</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ca</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>C</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp513120">Fyrir þetta efnahvarf:</para>
<equation id="eip-478" class="unnumbered"><label/><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ca</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>C</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.96</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math>
</equation><para id="fs-idp513536">(sjá <link document="m68868">Appendix J</link>)</para>
<para id="fs-idp340688">Setjið uppgefinn styrk kalsíumjóna inn í leysnimargfeldislíkinguna og leysið fyrir styrk oxalats:</para>
<equation id="fs-idp347152" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>Q</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ca</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mtext>C</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>1.96</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>

<equation id="fs-idp356336" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mn>2.2</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>C</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2</m:mtext></m:msub><m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>1.96</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>

<equation id="fs-idp365472" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>C</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>1.96</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>2.2</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.3em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mtext>8.9</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math></equation>

<para id="fs-idp377504">Styrkur <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>C</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> = 8,9 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–7</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> er nauðsynlegur til að koma af stað útfellingu CaC<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub> við þessar aðstæður.</para><para id="fs-idp383648"><title>Kannið þekkingu ykkar</title>Ef lausn inniheldur 0,0020 mól af <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CrO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> á lítra, hvaða styrk Ag<sup>+</sup> jónar þarf að ná með því að bæta við föstu AgNO<sub>3</sub> áður en Ag<sub>2</sub>CrO<sub>4</sub> byrjar að falla út? Hunsið aukningu á rúmmáli við álagningu fasts silfurnítrats.</para>
<note id="fs-idp387952"><title>Answer:</title><para id="fs-idp388336">6,7 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–5</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para></note>
</example>
<figure id="CNX_Chem_15_01_Blood" class="scaled-down">
<media id="fs-idp500240" alt="A photograph is shown of 6 vials of blood resting on and near a black and white document. Two of the vials have purple caps, three have tan caps, and one has a red cap. Each has a label and the vials with tan caps have a small amount of an off-white material present in a layer at the base of the vial.">
<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_Chem_15_01_Blood.jpg"/>
</media>
<caption>Hægt er að bæta segavarnarlyfjum í blóð sem bindast Ca<sup>2+</sup> jónum í blóðsermi og koma í veg fyrir að blóðið storkni. (heimild: breyting á verki eftir Neeta Lind)</caption>
</figure>
<example id="fs-idp392704">
<para id="fs-idp392960"><title>Styrkur eftir útfellingu</title>Fatnaður sem þveginn er í vatni með manganstyrk [Mn<sup>2+</sup>(<emphasis effect="italics">aq</emphasis>)] yfir 0,1 mg/L (1,8 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–6</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>) getur litast af manganinu við oxun, en hægt er að minnka magn Mn<sup>2+</sup> í vatninu með því að bæta við basa til að fella út Mn(OH)<sub>2</sub>. Hvaða pH er krafist til að halda [Mn<sup>2+</sup>] jöfnum 1,8 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–6</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>?</para>
<para id="fs-idp399216"><title>Lausn</title>Upplausn Mn(OH)<sub>2</sub> er lýst með jöfnunni:</para>
<equation id="fs-idp400336" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Mn(OH)</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Mn</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>2OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="4em"/><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>2</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>13</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation><para id="fs-idp1156752">Við jafnvægi:</para>
<equation id="fs-idp1159600" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mtext>Mn</m:mtext><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp1164192">eða</para>
<equation id="fs-idp1164576" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mn>1.8</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>2</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>13</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation><para id="fs-idp1173408">svo</para>
<equation id="fs-idp1173792" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>3.3</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math></equation><para id="fs-idp1179472">Reiknið pH út frá pOH:</para>
<equation id="fs-idp1179904" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mtable><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mtext>pOH</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>−log</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>−log</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mn>3.3</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>3.48</m:mtext></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mtext>pH</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>14.00</m:mtext><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mtext>pOH</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>14.00</m:mtext><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mtext>3.48</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>10.52</m:mtext></m:mtd></m:mtr></m:mtable></m:math></equation><para id="fs-idp1190688">(lokaniðurstaða námunduð að einum markverðum staf, takmarkað af óvissu <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub>)</para><para id="fs-idp1193504"><title>Kannið þekkingu ykkar</title>Fyrsta skrefið í framleiðslu magnesíummálms er útfelling Mg(OH)<sub>2</sub> úr sjó með álagningu Ca(OH)<sub>2</sub>. Styrkur Mg<sup>2+</sup>(<emphasis effect="italics">aq</emphasis>) í sjó er 5,37 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–2</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>. Reiknið pH-gildið þar sem [Mg<sup>2+</sup>] er lækkað niður í 1,0 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–5</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>.</para>
<note id="fs-idp1200000"><title>Answer:</title><para id="fs-idp1200384">10,97</para></note>
</example>
<para id="fs-idp1200896">Í lausnum sem innihalda tvær eða fleiri jónir sem geta myndað torleyst efnasambönd með sömu mótjóninni er hægt að nota tilraunaaðferð sem kallast <term id="term-00001">sértæk útfelling (e. selective precipitation)</term> til að fjarlægja einstakar jónir úr lausninni. Með því að auka styrk mótjónarinnar á stýrðan hátt er hægt að fella út jónir úr lausninni hverja fyrir sig, að því gefnu að leysni efnasambanda þeirra sé nægilega ólíkur. Í lausnum með jöfnum styrk markjóna fellur jónin sem myndar torleystasta efnasambandið fyrst út (við lægsta styrk mótjónarinnar) og hinar jónirnar falla síðan út þegar leysni efnasambanda þeirra er náð. Til að sýna þessa tækni er í næsta dæmi lýst aðskilnaði tveggja halíðjóna með útfellingu annarrar sem silfursalt.</para>
<note id="fs-idp1215552" class="chemistry everyday-life">
<title>Hlutverk útfellingar í skólphreinsun</title>
<para id="fs-idp1216528">Leysnijafnvægi eru gagnleg verkfæri við meðhöndlun skólps sem fer fram í mannvirkjum sem geta meðhöndlað bæjarvatn í þínum borg eða bæ (<link target-id="CNX_Chem_15_01_Wastewater"/>). Nánar tiltekið er sértæk útfelling notuð til að fjarlægja mengunarefni úr skólpi áður en því er hleypt aftur út í náttúruleg vatnshlot. Til dæmis eru fosfatjónir <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>(PO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>3−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> oft til staðar í vatni sem losað er frá verksmiðjum. Mikið magn fosfats veldur ofvexti þörunga, sem hefur áhrif á magn súrefnis sem er í boði fyrir lífríki sjávar auk þess sem það gerir vatnið óhæft til manneldis.</para><figure id="CNX_Chem_15_01_Wastewater" class="scaled-down">
<media id="fs-idp1220944" class="scaled-down" alt="A color photograph is shown of a high volume wastewater treatment facility. Nineteen large circular pools of water undergoing treatment are visible across the center of the photograph. A building and parking lot are visible in the foreground.">
<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_Chem_15_01_Wastewater.jpg"/>
</media>
<caption>Skólphreinsistöðvar, eins og þessi, fjarlægja mengunarefni úr skólpi áður en vatninu er hleypt aftur út í náttúrulegt umhverfi. (heimild: „eutrophication&amp;hypoxia“/Wikimedia Commons)</caption>
</figure>
<para id="fs-idp1223232">Ein algeng leið til að fjarlægja fosföt úr vatni er með álagningu kalsíumhýdroxíðs, eða kalks, Ca(OH)<sub>2</sub>. Þegar vatnið verður basískara hvarfast kalsíumjónirnar við fosfatjónir og mynda hýdroxýlapatít, Ca<sub>5</sub>(PO4)<sub>3</sub>OH, sem fellur síðan út úr lausninni:</para><equation id="fs-idp1225152" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ca</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>3PO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>3−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ca</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub><m:msub><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>(PO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mtext>3</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mtext>·</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation><para id="fs-idp1234976">Vegna þess að magn kalsíumjóna sem bætt er við veldur ekki því að farið sé yfir leysnimargfeldi annarra kalsíumsalta, verða anjónir þessara salta eftir í skólpinu. Botnfallið er síðan fjarlægt með síun og vatnið er fært aftur í hlutlaust pH með álagningu CO<sub>2</sub> í endurkolsýringarferli. Einnig er hægt að nota önnur efni til að fjarlægja fosföt með útfellingu, þar á meðal járn(III)klóríð og álsúlfat.</para>
<para id="fs-idp1236048">Skoðaðu þessa <link url="http://openstax.org/l/16Wastewater">site</link> síðu til að fá frekari upplýsingar um hvernig fosfór er fjarlægður úr skólpi.</para>
</note>
<example id="fs-idp1242128">
<para id="fs-idp1242384"><title>Útfelling silfurhalíða</title>Lausn inniheldur 0,00010 mól af KBr og 0,10 mól af KCl á lítra. AgNO<sub>3</sub> er smám saman bætt út í þessa lausn. Hvað myndast fyrst, fast AgBr eða fast AgCl?</para>
<para id="fs-idp1243456"><title>Lausn</title>Jafnvægin tvö sem um ræðir eru:</para>
<equation id="fs-idp1244144" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtable><m:mtr><m:mtd columnalign="center"><m:mtext>AgCl</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ag</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Cl</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd/><m:mtd/><m:mtd columnalign="right"><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo>=</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mtext>1.6</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr><m:mtd columnalign="center"><m:mtext>AgBr</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ag</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mtext>Br</m:mtext><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd/><m:mtd/><m:mtd columnalign="right"><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mo>=</m:mo></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mtext>5.0</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>13</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mtd></m:mtr></m:mtable></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp15236832">Ef lausnin innihéldi um það bil <emphasis effect="italics">jafnan</emphasis> styrk af Cl<sup>–</sup> og Br<sup>–</sup>, þá myndi silfursaltið með lægra <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> (AgBr) falla út fyrst. Styrkurinn er þó ekki jafn, þannig að reikna þarf út [Ag<sup>+</sup>] þar sem AgCl byrjar að falla út og [Ag<sup>+</sup>] þar sem AgBr byrjar að falla út. Saltið sem myndast við lægri [Ag<sup>+</sup>] fellur út fyrst.</para>
<para id="fs-idp15240992">AgBr fellur út þegar <emphasis effect="italics">Q</emphasis> er jafnt og <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> fyrir AgBr</para>
<equation id="fs-idp15244832" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>Q</m:mi><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mtext>Ag</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mtext>Br</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mtext>Ag</m:mtext><m:mn>+</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mtext>(0.00010)</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>5.0</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>13</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<equation id="fs-idp15252336" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ag</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mtext>5.0</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>13</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>0.00010</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>5.0</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math></equation><para id="fs-idp15261056">AgBr byrjar að falla út þegar [Ag<sup>+</sup>] er 5,0 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–9</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>.</para>
<para id="fs-idp15263392">Fyrir AgCl: AgCl fellur út þegar <emphasis effect="italics">Q</emphasis> er jafnt og <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> fyrir AgCl (1,6 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–10</sup>). Þegar [Cl<sup>–</sup>] = 0,10 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>:</para>
<equation id="fs-idp15267232" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>Q</m:mi><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ag</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mtext>Cl</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ag</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mtext>(0.10)</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>1.6</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation><equation id="fs-idp15275248" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ag</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>1.6</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>0.10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>1.6</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math></equation><para id="fs-idp15284336">AgCl byrjar að falla út þegar [Ag<sup>+</sup>] er 1,6 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–9</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>.</para><para id="fs-idp15286672">AgCl byrjar að falla út við lægri [Ag<sup>+</sup>] en AgBr, þannig að AgCl byrjar að falla út fyrst. Athugið að styrkur klóríðjóna í upphaflegu efnablöndunni var marktækt meiri en styrkur brómíðjóna og því féll silfurklóríð út fyrst þrátt fyrir að hafa hærra <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> en silfurbrómíð.</para>
<para id="fs-idp15287568"><title>Kannaðu þekkingu þína</title>Ef silfurnítratlausn er bætt út í lausn sem er 0,050 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> í bæði Cl<sup>–</sup> og Br<sup>–</sup> jónum, við hvaða [Ag<sup>+</sup>] myndi útfelling hefjast og hver væri formúla botnfallsins?</para>
<note id="fs-idp15290048"><title>Answer:</title><para id="fs-idp15290432">[Ag<sup>+</sup>] = 1,0 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–11</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>; AgBr fellur út fyrst</para></note>
</example>
</section>
<section id="fs-idp15293024">
<title>Samjónahrif</title>
<para id="fs-idp15293696">Í samanburði við hreint vatn er leysni jónaefnis minni í vatnslausnum sem innihalda <emphasis effect="italics">samjón</emphasis> (jón sem einnig myndast við upplausn jónaefnisins). Þetta er dæmi um fyrirbæri sem kallast <emphasis effect="bold">samjónahrif</emphasis>, sem er afleiðing massavirknilögmálsins sem hægt er að útskýra með lögmáli Le Châteliers. Lítum á upplausn silfurjoðíðs:</para>
<equation id="fs-idp15306976" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>AgI</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ag</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mtext>I</m:mtext><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp15314160">Þetta leysnijafnvægi getur hliðrast til vinstri með álagningu annaðhvort silfur(I)- eða joðíðjóna, sem leiðir til útfellingar AgI og lægri styrks uppleystra Ag<sup>+</sup> og I<sup>–</sup>. Í lausnum sem þegar innihalda aðra hvora þessara jóna getur minna AgI leyst upp en í lausnum án þessara jóna.</para>
<para id="fs-idm386466432">Þessi áhrif má einnig útskýra með tilliti til massavirkni eins og hún er sett fram í leysnimargfeldisjöfnunni:</para>
<equation id="fs-idm386465920" class="unnumbered"><m:math>
<m:mrow>
<m:msub>
<m:mi>K</m:mi>
<m:mrow>
<m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow>
</m:msub>
<m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup>
<m:mrow>
<m:mtext>Ag</m:mtext></m:mrow>
<m:mo>+</m:mo>
</m:msup>
<m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup>
<m:mtext>I</m:mtext>
<m:mo>−</m:mo>
</m:msup>
<m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow>
</m:math>
</equation>
<para id="fs-idm386458688">Stærðfræðilegt margfeldi mólarstyrks silfurs(I) og joðíðjóna er fasti í jafnvægisblöndu <emphasis effect="italics">óháð uppruna jónanna</emphasis>, og því verður aukning á styrk einnar jónar að vega upp á móti með samsvarandi minnkun á hinni.</para>
<note id="fs-idp1237920" class="chemistry link-to-learning">
<para id="fs-idp1239856">Skoðaðu þessa <link url="http://openstax.org/l/16solublesalts">hermun</link> til að kanna ýmsa þætti samjónahrifa.</para>
</note>
<example id="fs-idp11083040">
<para id="fs-idp11083296"><title>Samjónahrif á leysni</title>Hver eru áhrifin á magn fasts Mg(OH)<sub>2</sub> og styrk Mg<sup>2+</sup> og OH<sup>–</sup> þegar eftirfarandi er bætt við mettaða lausn af Mg(OH)<sub>2</sub>?</para>
<para id="fs-idp11085600">(a) MgCl<sub>2</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idp11086240">(b) KOH</para>
<para id="fs-idp11087008">(c) NaNO<sub>3</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idp11087648">(d) Mg(OH)<sub>2</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idp11088288"><title>Lausn</title>Leysnijafnvægið er</para>
<equation id="fs-idp141736144" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>Mg</m:mtext><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Mg</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idm745168">(a) Með því að bæta við samjón, Mg<sup>2+</sup>, eykst styrkur þessarar jónar og leysnijafnvægið hliðrast til vinstri, sem minnkar styrk hýdroxíðjónarinnar og eykur magn óuppleysts magnesíumhýdroxíðs.</para>
<para id="fs-idm743248">(b) Með því að bæta við samjón, OH<sup>–</sup>, eykst styrkur þessarar jónar og leysnijafnvægið hliðrast til vinstri, sem minnkar styrk magnesíumjónarinnar og eykur magn óuppleysts magnesíumhýdroxíðs.</para>
<para id="fs-idm330455632">(c) Efnasambandið sem bætt er við inniheldur ekki samjón og engin áhrif eru væntanleg á leysnijafnvægi magnesíumhýdroxíðs.</para>
<para id="fs-idm330455104">(d) Með því að bæta við meira föstu magnesíumhýdroxíði eykst magn óuppleysts efnasambands í efnablöndunni. Lausnin er þó þegar mettuð, þannig að styrkur uppleystra magnesíum- og hýdroxíðjóna helst óbreyttur.</para>
<equation id="fs-idm740800" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>Q</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Mg</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idm735616">Þannig hefur breyting á magni fasts magnesíumhýdroxíðs í efnablöndunni engin áhrif á gildi <emphasis effect="italics">Q</emphasis> og engin hliðrun er nauðsynleg til að endurheimta <emphasis effect="italics">Q</emphasis> að gildi jafnvægisfastans.</para>
<para id="fs-idm701008"><title>Kannaðu þekkingu þína</title>Hver eru áhrifin á magn fasts NiCO<sub>3</sub> og styrk Ni<sup>2+</sup> og <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> þegar eftirfarandi er bætt við mettaða lausn af NiCO<sub>3</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idm697184">(a) Ni(NO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idm696160">(b) KClO<sub>4</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idm695520">(c) NiCO<sub>3</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idm694880">(d) K<sub>2</sub>CO<sub>3</sub></para>
<note id="fs-idm690608"><title>Answer:</title>
<para id="fs-idm690096">(a) massi NiCO<sub>3</sub>(<emphasis effect="italics">s</emphasis>) eykst, [Ni<sup>2+</sup>] eykst, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> minnkar; (b) engin teljandi áhrif; (c) engin áhrif nema að auka magn fasts NiCO<sub>3</sub>; (d) massi NiCO<sub>3</sub>(<emphasis effect="italics">s</emphasis>) eykst, [Ni<sup>2+</sup>] minnkar, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> eykst;</para>
</note>
</example>
<example id="fs-idp15318512">
<para id="fs-idp15318768"><title>Samjónahrif</title>Reiknaðu mólarleysni kadmíumsúlfíðs (CdS) í 0,010-<emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> lausn af kadmíumbrómíði (CdBr<sub>2</sub>). <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> fyrir CdS er 1,0 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–28</sup>.</para>
<para id="fs-idp15322272"><title>Lausn</title>Þennan útreikning má framkvæma með ICE-aðferðinni:</para>
<equation id="fs-idp15323568" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>CdS</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Cd</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mtext>S</m:mtext><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<media id="fs-idp15331040" class="scaled-down" alt="This table has two main columns and four rows. The first row for the first column does not have a heading and then has the following in the first column: Initial concentration ( M ), Change ( M ), and Equilibrium concentration ( M ). The second column has the header, “C d S equilibrium arrow C d to the second power plus S to the second power superscript negative sign.” Under the second column is a subgroup of three rows and three columns. The first column is blank. The second column has the following: 0.010, positive x, 0.010 plus x. The third column has the following: 0, positive x, x.">
<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_Chem_15_01_ICETable3_img.jpg"/>
</media>
<equation id="fs-idp15332448" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Cd</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mtext>S</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.0</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>28</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<equation id="fs-idp13457936" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mn>0.010</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>1.0</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>28</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idm394907456">Vegna þess að <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> er mjög lítið, gerum við ráð fyrir að <emphasis effect="italics">x</emphasis> &lt;&lt; 0,010 og leysum einfölduðu jöfnuna fyrir <emphasis effect="italics">x</emphasis>:</para>
<equation id="fs-idp13479456" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mn>0.010</m:mn><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>1.0</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>28</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<equation id="fs-idp13485120" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>1.0</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>26</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp13488544">Mólarleysni CdS í þessari lausn er 1,0 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–26</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>.</para>
<para id="fs-idp13490448"><title>Kannaðu þekkingu þína</title>Reiknaðu mólarleysni álhýdroxíðs, Al(OH)<sub>3</sub>, í 0,015-<emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> lausn af álnítrati, Al(NO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>3</sub>. <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> fyrir Al(OH)<sub>3</sub> er 2 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–32</sup>.</para>
<note id="fs-idp13495104"><title>Answer:</title><para id="fs-idp13495488">4 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–11</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para></note></example>
</section>
<section id="fs-idp13497520" class="summary">
<title>Lykilhugtök og samantekt</title>
<para id="fs-idp13498448">Jafnvægisfastinn fyrir jafnvægi sem felur í sér útfellingu eða upplausn á örlítið auðleystu jónaföstu efni er kallaður leysnimargfeldi, <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub>, fasta efnisins. Fyrir misleitt jafnvægi sem felur í sér örlítið auðleysta fasta efnið M<sub><emphasis effect="italics">p</sub></emphasis>X<sub><emphasis effect="italics">q</sub></emphasis> og jónir þess M<sup>m+</sup> og X<sup>n–</sup>:</para>
<equation id="fs-idp13501568" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext>M</m:mtext><m:mi>p</m:mi></m:msub><m:msub><m:mtext>X</m:mtext><m:mi>q</m:mi></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:mi>p</m:mi><m:msup><m:mtext>M</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mtext>m+</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:msup><m:mtext>X</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mtext>n−</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp13510416">er leysnimargfeldisjafnan:</para>
<equation id="fs-idp13510864" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>[M</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mtext>m+</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mi>p</m:mi></m:msup><m:msup><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>[X</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mtext>n−</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mi>q</m:mi></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp13516480">Leysnimargfeldi örlítið auðleysts rafkleyfa er hægt að reikna út frá leysni hans; öfugt er hægt að reikna leysni hans út frá <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub>, að því gefnu að eina marktæka efnahvarfið sem á sér stað þegar fasta efnið leysist upp sé myndun jóna þess.</para>
<para id="fs-idp13518032">Örlítið auðleystur rafkleyfi byrjar að falla út þegar stærð hvarfstuðulsins fyrir upplausnarhvarfið fer yfir stærð leysnimargfeldisins. Útfelling heldur áfram þar til hvarfstuðullinn er jafn leysnimargfeldinu.</para>
</section>
<section id="fs-idp13519952" class="key-equations">
<title>Lykiljafna</title>
<table id="key-equations-table" class="unnumbered unstyled" summary="key equations table"><label/>
<tgroup cols="1"><colspec colnum="1" colname="c1"/>
<tbody>
<row><entry><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext>M</m:mtext><m:mi>p</m:mi></m:msub><m:msub><m:mtext>X</m:mtext><m:mi>q</m:mi></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:mi>p</m:mi><m:msup><m:mtext>M</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mtext>m+</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:msup><m:mtext>X</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mtext>n−</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="4em"/><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mtext>M</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>m+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mi>p</m:mi></m:msup><m:msup><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mtext>X</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mtext>n−</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mi>q</m:mi></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></entry>
</row>
</tbody></tgroup></table>
</section>
<section id="fs-idp13535408" class="exercises">
<title>Efnafræði – verkefni í lok kafla</title>
<exercise id="fs-idp13536336">
<problem id="fs-idp13536464">
<para id="fs-idp13536592">Ljúktu við breytingar á styrk fyrir hvert eftirfarandi efnahvarfa:</para>
<para id="fs-idp13536976">(a)<newline/> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtable><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mtext>AgI</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⟶</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow>
<m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ag</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mspace width="0.2em"/>
<m:msup><m:mtext>I</m:mtext><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr/><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mrow/></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mo>_____</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd></m:mtr></m:mtable></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp13548352">(b)<newline/> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtable><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CaCO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⟶</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow>
<m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ca</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub>
<m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr/><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mrow/></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mo>____</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mtd></m:mtr></m:mtable></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp13561168">(c)<newline/> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtable><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mtext>Mg</m:mtext><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⟶</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow>
<m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Mg</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn>
<m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr/><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mrow/></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mo>_____</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd></m:mtr></m:mtable></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp13575072">(d)<newline/> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtable>
    <m:mtr>
      <m:mtd><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Mg</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>PO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⟶</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/></m:mrow></m:mtd>
      <m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Mg</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd>
      <m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>PO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>3−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd></m:mtr>
      <m:mtr/>
      <m:mtr>
        <m:mtd><m:mrow/></m:mtd>
        <m:mtd><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mtd>
        <m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mo>_____</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd>
      </m:mtr>
    </m:mtable></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp13591056">(e)<newline/> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtable><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ca</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>PO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⟶</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ca</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>PO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>3−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr/><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mrow/></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mo>_____</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mo>_____</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mtd></m:mtr></m:mtable></m:mrow></m:math></para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp13611616">
<para id="fs-idp272577456">(a)<newline/> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtable><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mtext>AgI</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ag</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mtext>I</m:mtext><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr/><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mrow/></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:munder accentunder="true"><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="true">_</m:mo></m:munder></m:mrow></m:mtd></m:mtr></m:mtable></m:mrow></m:math><newline/> (b)<newline/> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtable><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CaCO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ca</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr/><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mrow/></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:munder accentunder="true"><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="true">_</m:mo></m:munder></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mtd></m:mtr></m:mtable></m:mrow></m:math><newline/> (c)<newline/> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtable columnalign="left"><m:mtr columnalign="left"><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mrow><m:mtext>Mg</m:mtext><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Mg</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mrow><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr columnalign="left"><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mrow/></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mtd><m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mrow><m:munder accentunder="true"><m:mrow><m:mtext>2</m:mtext><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="true">_</m:mo></m:munder></m:mrow></m:mtd></m:mtr></m:mtable></m:mrow></m:math><newline/> (d)<newline/> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtable><m:mtr>
<m:mtd><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Mg</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>PO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>3Mg</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>2PO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>3−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd></m:mtr>
<m:mtr/>
<m:mtr>
  <m:mtd><m:mrow/></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:munder accentunder="true"><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="true">_</m:mo></m:munder></m:mrow></m:mtd>
  <m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow>
</m:mtd></m:mtr></m:mtable></m:mrow></m:math><newline/> (e)<newline/> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtable><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ca</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>PO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>5Ca</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>3PO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>3−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr/><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mrow/></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:munder accentunder="true"><m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="true">_</m:mo></m:munder></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:munder accentunder="true"><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="true">_</m:mo></m:munder></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mtd></m:mtr></m:mtable></m:mrow></m:math></para></solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp15620912">
<problem id="fs-idp15621040">
<para id="fs-idp15621168">Ljúktu við breytingar á styrk fyrir hvert eftirfarandi efnahvarfa:</para>
<para id="fs-idp15621552">(a)<newline/> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtable><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>BaSO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⟶</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ba</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>SO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr/><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mrow/></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mo>_____</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd></m:mtr></m:mtable></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp15634624">(b<newline/> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtable><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ag</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>SO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⟶</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ag</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>SO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr/><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mrow/></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mo>_____</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mtd></m:mtr></m:mtable></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp15648336">(c)<newline/> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtable><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mtext>Al</m:mtext><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⟶</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Al</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>3+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr/><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mrow/></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mo>_____</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd></m:mtr></m:mtable></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp15662240">(d)<newline/> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtable><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mtext>Pb</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mtext>Cl</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⟶</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Pb</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Cl</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr/><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mrow/></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mo>_____</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mo>_____</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd></m:mtr></m:mtable></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp15680448">(e)<newline/> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtable><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ca</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>AsO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⟶</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ca</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>AsO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>3−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr/><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mrow/></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mo>_____</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mtd></m:mtr></m:mtable></m:mrow></m:math></para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp15761856">
<problem id="fs-idp15761984">
<para id="fs-idp15762112">Hvernig breytist styrkur Ag<sup>+</sup> og <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CrO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> í mettaðri lausn yfir 1,0 g af föstu Ag<sub>2</sub>CrO<sub>4</sub> þegar 100 g af föstu Ag<sub>2</sub>CrO<sub>4</sub> er bætt við kerfið? Útskýrðu.</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp15766576">
<para id="fs-idp15766832">Engin breyting verður. Fast efni hefur virknina 1, hvort sem það er lítið eða mikið af því.</para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp15767216">
<problem id="fs-idp15767344">
<para id="fs-idp15767472">Hvernig breytist styrkur Pb<sup>2+</sup> og S<sup>2–</sup> þegar K<sub>2</sub>S er bætt við mettaða lausn af PbS?</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp15771216">
<problem id="fs-idp15771344">
<para id="fs-idp15771472">Hvaða viðbótarupplýsingar þurfum við til að svara eftirfarandi spurningu: Hvernig hefur hækkun hitastigs áhrif á jafnvægi fasts silfurbrómíðs við mettaða lausn af jónum þess?</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp15772192">
<para id="fs-idp15772448">Leysni silfurbrómíðs við nýja hitastigið verður að vera þekkt. Venjulega eykst leysnin og eitthvað af fasta silfurbrómíðinu leysist upp.</para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp15773008">
<problem id="fs-idp15773136">
<para id="fs-idp15773264">Hvert eftirfarandi örlítið auðleystu efnasambanda hefur meiri leysni en reiknað er út frá leysnimargfeldi þess vegna vatnsrofs anjónarinnar sem er til staðar: CoSO<sub>3</sub>, CuI, PbCO<sub>3</sub>, PbCl<sub>2</sub>, Tl<sub>2</sub>S, KClO<sub>4</sub>?</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp15777680">
<problem id="fs-idp15777808">
<para id="fs-idp15777936">Hvert eftirfarandi örlítið auðleystu efnasambanda hefur meiri leysni en reiknað er út frá leysnimargfeldi þess vegna vatnsrofs anjónarinnar sem er til staðar: AgCl, BaSO<sub>4</sub>, CaF<sub>2</sub>, Hg<sub>2</sub>I<sub>2</sub>, MnCO<sub>3</sub> og ZnS?</para></problem>
<solution id="fs-idp15780560">
<para id="fs-idp15780816">CaF<sub>2</sub>, MnCO<sub>3</sub> og ZnS</para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp15782160">
<problem id="fs-idp15782288">
<para id="fs-idp15782416">Skrifaðu jónajöfnuna fyrir upplausn og leysnimargfeldisjöfnuna (<emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub>) fyrir hvert eftirfarandi örlítið auðleystu jónaefnasambanda:</para>
<para id="fs-idp15783680">(a) PbCl<sub>2</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idp15784320">(b) Ag<sub>2</sub>S</para>
<para id="fs-idp15785088">(c) Sr<sub>3</sub>(PO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idp15786496">(d) SrSO<sub>4</sub></para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp13118608">
<problem id="fs-idp13118736">
<para id="fs-idp13118864">Skrifaðu jónajöfnuna fyrir upplausnina og <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub>-jöfnuna fyrir hvert eftirfarandi örlítið auðleystu jónaefnasambanda:</para>
<para id="fs-idp13120192">(a) LaF<sub>3</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idp13120832">(b) CaCO<sub>3</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idp13121472">(c) Ag<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>4</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idp13122496">(d) Pb(OH)<sub>2</sub></para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp13123264">
<para id="fs-idp13123520">(a) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>LaF</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>La</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>3+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>3F</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="4em"/><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>La</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>3+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mtext>F</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>;</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math><newline/> (b) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CaCO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ca</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="4em"/><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ca</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>;</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math><newline/> (c) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ag</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>SO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>2Ag</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>SO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="4em"/><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ag</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>SO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>;</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math><newline/> (d) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Pb(OH)</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Pb</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>2OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="4em"/><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Pb</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp13178304">
<problem id="fs-idp13178432">
<para id="fs-idp13178560">Í <emphasis effect="italics"><link url="http://openstax.org/l/16Handbook</emphasis>">Handbook of Chemistry and Physics</link> er leysni eftirfarandi efnasambanda gefinn upp í grömmum á 100 ml af vatni. Þar sem þessi efnasambönd eru aðeins örlítið leysanleg skal gera ráð fyrir að rúmmálið breytist ekki við upplausn og reikna leysnimargfeldi fyrir hvert þeirra.</para>
<para id="fs-idp13180272">(a) BaSiF<sub>6</sub>, 0,026 g/100 ml (inniheldur <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>SiF</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> jónir)</para>
<para id="fs-idp13182912">(b) Ce(IO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>4</sub>, 1,5 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–2</sup> g/100 ml</para>
<para id="fs-idp13184960">(c) Gd<sub>2</sub>(SO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>3</sub>, 3,98 g/100 ml</para>
<para id="fs-idp13186496">(d) (NH<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub>PtBr<sub>6</sub>, 0,59 g/100 ml (inniheldur <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>PtBr</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> jónir)</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp13270928">
<problem id="fs-idp13271056">
<para id="fs-idp13271184">Í <emphasis effect="italics"><link url="http://openstax.org/l/16Handbook</emphasis>">Handbook of Chemistry and Physics</link> er leysni eftirfarandi efnasambanda gefinn upp í grömmum á 100 ml af vatni. Þar sem þessi efnasambönd eru aðeins örlítið leysanleg skal gera ráð fyrir að rúmmálið breytist ekki við upplausn og reikna leysnimargfeldi fyrir hvert þeirra.</para>
<para id="fs-idp13273024">(a) BaSeO<sub>4</sub>, 0,0118 g/100 ml</para>
<para id="fs-idp13273824">(b) Ba(BrO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>·H<sub>2</sub>O, 0,30 g/100 ml</para>
<para id="fs-idp13275424">(c) NH<sub>4</sub>MgAsO<sub>4</sub>·6H<sub>2</sub>O, 0,038 g/100 ml</para>
<para id="fs-idp13277024">(d) La<sub>2</sub>(MoO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>3</sub>, 0,00179 g/100 ml</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp13278720">
<para id="fs-idp53571088">(a) 1,77 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–7</sup>; (b) 1,6 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–6</sup>; (c) 2,2 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–9</sup>; (d) 7,91 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–22</sup></para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp13349584">
<problem id="fs-idp13349712">
<para id="fs-idp13349840">Notið leysnimargfeldi og spáið fyrir um hvaða af eftirfarandi söltum er auðleystast, miðað við mól á lítra, í hreinu vatni: CaF<sub>2</sub>, Hg<sub>2</sub>Cl<sub>2</sub>, PbI<sub>2</sub> eða Sn(OH)<sub>2</sub>.</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp13365680">
<problem id="fs-idp13365808">
<para id="fs-idp13365936">Miðað við að engin önnur jafnvægi en upplausn eigi sér stað, reiknið mólarleysni hvers eftirfarandi efnis út frá leysnimargfeldi þess:</para>
<para id="fs-idp13366480">(a) KHC<sub>4</sub>H<sub>4</sub>O<sub>6</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idp13367888">(b) PbI<sub>2</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idp13368528">(c) Ag<sub>4</sub>[Fe(CN)<sub>6</sub>], salt sem inniheldur <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Fe(CN)</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>4–</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> jónina</para><para id="fs-idp13371392">(d) Hg<sub>2</sub>I<sub>2</sub></para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp13372544">
<para id="fs-idp13372800">(a) 2 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–2</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>; (b) 1,5 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>; (c) 2,27 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–9</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>; (d) 2,2 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–10</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para></solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp13415712">
<problem id="fs-idp13415840">
<para id="fs-idp13415968">Miðað við að engin önnur jafnvægi en upplausn eigi sér stað, reiknið mólarleysni hvers eftirfarandi efnis út frá leysnimargfeldi þess:</para>
<para id="fs-idp13416512">(a) Ag<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>4</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idp13417536">(b) PbBr<sub>2</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idp13418176">(c) AgI</para>
<para id="fs-idp13418560">(d) CaC<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub>·H<sub>2</sub>O</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp14208112">
<problem id="fs-idp14208240">
<para id="fs-idp14208368">Miðað við að engin önnur jafnvægi en upplausn eigi sér stað, reiknið styrk allra tegunda leystra efna í hverri af eftirfarandi lausnum af söltum í snertingu við lausn sem inniheldur sameiginlega jón. Sýnið fram á að hægt sé að vanrækja breytingar á upphafsstyrk sameiginlegu jónanna.</para>
<para id="fs-idp14209056">(a) AgCl(<emphasis effect="italics">s</emphasis>) í 0,025 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> NaCl</para>
<para id="fs-idp14210688">(b) CaF<sub>2</sub>(<emphasis effect="italics">s</emphasis>) í 0,00133 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> KF</para>
<para id="fs-idp14212704">(c) Ag<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>4</sub>(<emphasis effect="italics">s</emphasis>) í 0,500 L af lausn sem inniheldur 19,50 g af K<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>4</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idp14215184">(d) Zn(OH)<sub>2</sub>(<emphasis effect="italics">s</emphasis>) í lausn með stuðpúða við pH 11,45</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp14216768">
<para id="fs-idp14217024">(a) 6,4 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−9</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> = [Ag<sup>+</sup>], [Cl<sup>−</sup>] = 0,025 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>. Athugun: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>6.4</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.3em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.3em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>0.025</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mtext>100%</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>2.6</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mi>%</m:mi><m:mo>,</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>óveruleg breyting;<newline/> (b) 2,2 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−5</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> = [Ca<sup>2+</sup>], [F<sup>−</sup>] = 0,0013 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>. Athugun: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mtext>2.26</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>0.00133</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mtext>100%</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>1.70%</m:mtext><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> Þetta gildi er minna en 5% og má hunsa það.<newline/> (c) 0,2238 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> = <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>SO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>;</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> [Ag<sup>+</sup>] = 7,4 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>. Athugun: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>3.7</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>0.2238</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mn>100</m:mn><m:mi>%</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>1.64</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo>;</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> skilyrðið er uppfyllt.<newline/> (d) [OH<sup>–</sup>] = 2,8 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>; 5,7 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−12</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> = [Zn<sup>2+</sup>]. Athugun: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>5.7</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>2.8</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:mfrac><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mtext>100%</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>2.0</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mi>%</m:mi><m:mo>;</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> <emphasis effect="italics">x</emphasis> er minna en 5% af [OH<sup>–</sup>] og er því óverulegt.</para></solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp14351088">
<problem id="fs-idp14351216">
<para id="fs-idp14351344">Gefið að engin önnur jafnvægi en upplausn eigi sér stað, reiknið styrk allra tegunda leystra efna í hverri af eftirfarandi lausnum salta í snertingu við lausn sem inniheldur sameiginlega jón. Sýnið fram á að breytingar á upphafsstyrk sameiginlegu jónanna megi hunsa.</para>
<para id="fs-idp14352032">(a) TlCl(<emphasis effect="italics">s</emphasis>) í 1,250 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> HCl</para>
<para id="fs-idp14353664">(b) PbI<sub>2</sub>(<emphasis effect="italics">s</emphasis>) í 0,0355 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> CaI<sub>2</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idp14355936">(c) Ag<sub>2</sub>CrO<sub>4</sub>(<emphasis effect="italics">s</emphasis>) í 0,225 L af lausn sem inniheldur 0,856 g af K<sub>2</sub>CrO<sub>4</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idp14358416">(d) Cd(OH)<sub>2</sub>(<emphasis effect="italics">s</emphasis>) í lausn með stuðpúða við pH 10,995</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp14499248">
<problem id="fs-idp14499376">
<para id="fs-idp14499504">Gefið að engin önnur jafnvægi en upplausn eigi sér stað, reiknið styrk allra tegunda leystra efna í hverri af eftirfarandi lausnum salta í snertingu við lausn sem inniheldur sameiginlega jón. Takið fram hvort viðeigandi sé að hunsa breytingar á upphafsstyrk sameiginlegu jónanna.</para>
<para id="fs-idp14500224">(a) TlCl(<emphasis effect="italics">s</emphasis>) í 0,025 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> TlNO<sub>3</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idp14502112">(b) BaF<sub>2</sub>(<emphasis effect="italics">s</emphasis>) í 0,313 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> KF</para>
<para id="fs-idp14504128">(c) MgC<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub> í 2,250 L af lausn sem inniheldur 8,156 g af Mg(NO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idp14505984">(d) Ca(OH)<sub>2</sub>(<emphasis effect="italics">s</emphasis>) í lausn án stuðpúða með upphafs-pH 12,700</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp14507504">
<para id="fs-idp272462288">(a) Ekki má hunsa breytingu á upphafsstyrk sameiginlegrar jónar (verður að leysa annars stigs jöfnu)<newline/> [Ti<sup>+</sup>] = 0,031 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis><newline/> [Cl<sup>–</sup>] = 0,0056 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> (b) Má hunsa breytingu á upphafsstyrk sameiginlegrar jónar.<newline/> [Ba<sup>2+</sup>] = 2,4 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–4</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis><newline/> [F<sup>–</sup>] = 0,313 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>;<newline/> (c) Má hunsa breytingu á upphafsstyrk sameiginlegrar jónar.<newline/> [Mg<sup>2+</sup>] = 0,0244 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis><newline/> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>C</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2.9</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mtext>−5</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math><newline/> (d) Má hunsa breytingu á upphafsstyrk sameiginlegrar jónar.<newline/> [Ca<sup>2+</sup>] = 5,18 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–4</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis><newline/> [C<sub>2</sub>)<sub>4</sub><sup>2–</sup>] = 0,051 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para></solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp14702288">
<problem id="fs-idp14702416">
<para id="fs-idp14702544">Útskýrið hvers vegna má hunsa breytingar á styrk sameiginlegu jónanna í <link target-id="fs-idp14499248"/>.</para></problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp14703872">
<problem id="fs-idp14704000">
<para id="fs-idp14704128">Útskýrið hvers vegna ekki má hunsa breytingar á styrk sameiginlegu jónanna í <link target-id="fs-idp14702288"/>.</para></problem>
<solution id="fs-idp14704752">
<para id="fs-idp14705008">Breytingarnar á styrk eru meiri en 5% og fara því yfir hámarksgildið til að hunsa breytinguna.</para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp14705520">
<problem id="fs-idp14705648">
<para id="fs-idp14705776">Reiknið leysni álhýdroxíðs, Al(OH)<sub>3</sub>, í lausn með stuðpúða við pH 11,00.</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp14726720">
<problem id="fs-idp14726848">
<para id="fs-idp14726976">Sjá <link document="m68868">Appendix J</link> fyrir leysnimargfeldi kalsíumsalta. Ákvarðið hvaða af skráðu kalsíumsöltunum er auðleystast í mólum á lítra og hvaða er auðleystast í grömmum á lítra.</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp14728544">
<para id="fs-idp14728800">CaSO<sub>4</sub>∙2H<sub>2</sub>O er auðleystasta Ca-saltið í mól/L og það er einnig auðleystasta Ca-saltið í g/L.</para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp14816032">
<problem id="fs-idp14816160">
<para id="fs-idp14816288">Flest baríumefnasambönd eru mjög eitruð; hins vegar er baríumsúlfat oft gefið innvortis sem hjálpartæki við röntgenrannsókn á neðri hluta meltingarvegar (<link target-id="CNX_Chem_15_01_BariumXray"/>). Þessi notkun á BaSO<sub>4</sub> er möguleg vegna lítillar leysni þess. Reiknaðu mólarleysni BaSO<sub>4</sub> og massa baríums sem er til staðar í 1,00 L af vatni sem er mettað af BaSO<sub>4</sub>.</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp14846704">
<problem id="fs-idp14846832">
<para id="fs-idp14846960">Staðlar lýðheilsustofnunar fyrir drykkjarvatn setja hámark 250 mg/L (2,60 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>) af <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>SO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> vegna hægðalosandi áhrifa þess. Uppfyllir náttúrulegt vatn sem er mettað af CaSO<sub>4</sub> („gipsvatn“) vegna þess að það fer í gegnum jarðveg sem inniheldur gifs, CaSO<sub>4</sub>·2H<sub>2</sub>O, þessa staðla? Hver er styrkur <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>SO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> í slíku vatni?</para></problem>
<solution id="fs-idp14853504">
<para id="fs-idp14853760">7,8 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> = <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>SO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> = [Ca<sup>2+</sup>]; Þar sem þessi styrkur er hærri en 2,60 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>, uppfyllir „gipsvatn“ ekki staðlana.</para></solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp14880288">
<problem id="fs-idp14880416">
<para id="fs-idp14880544">Framkvæmdu eftirfarandi útreikninga:</para>
<para id="fs-idp14880976">(a) Reiknaðu [Ag<sup>+</sup>] í mettaðri vatnslausn af AgBr.</para>
<para id="fs-idp14881840">(b) Hver verður [Ag<sup>+</sup>] þegar nægu KBr hefur verið bætt við til að gera [Br<sup>–</sup>] = 0,050 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>?</para>
<para id="fs-idp14883712">(c) Hver verður [Br<sup>–</sup>] þegar nægu AgNO<sub>3</sub> hefur verið bætt við til að gera [Ag<sup>+</sup>] = 0,020 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>?</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp14922048">
<problem id="fs-idp14922176">
<para id="fs-idp14922304">Leysnimargfeldi CaSO<sub>4</sub>·2H<sub>2</sub>O er 2,4 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–5</sup>. Hversu mikill massi af þessu salti leysist upp í 1,0 L af 0,010 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext>SO</m:mtext><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>?</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp14927136">
<para id="fs-idp14927392">Massi (CaSO<sub>4</sub>·2H<sub>2</sub>O) = 0,72 g</para></solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp14989248">
<problem id="fs-idp14989376">
<para id="fs-idp14989504">Miðað við að engin önnur jafnvægi en upplausn eigi sér stað, reiknaðu styrk jóna í mettaðri lausn af hverju eftirfarandi efna (sjá <link document="m68868">viðauka J</link> fyrir leysnimargfeldi).</para>
<para id="fs-idp14990976">(a) TlCl</para>
<para id="fs-idp14991360">(b) BaF<sub>2</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idp14992000">(c) Ag<sub>2</sub>CrO<sub>4</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idp14993024">(d) CaC<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub>·H<sub>2</sub>O</para>
<para id="fs-idp14994560">(e) steinefnið anglesít, PbSO<sub>4</sub></para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp15085264">
<problem id="fs-idp15085392">
<para id="fs-idp15085520">Miðað við að engin önnur jafnvægi en upplausn eigi sér stað, reiknaðu styrk jóna í mettaðri lausn af hverju eftirfarandi efna (sjá <link document="m68868">viðauka J</link> fyrir leysnimargfeldi):</para>
<para id="fs-idp15086992">(a) AgI</para>
<para id="fs-idp15087376">(b) Ag<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>4</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idp15088400">(c) Mn(OH)<sub>2</sub></para>
<para id="fs-idp15089040">(d) Sr(OH)<sub>2</sub>·8H<sub>2</sub>O</para>
<para id="fs-idp15090192">(e) steinefnið brúsít, Mg(OH)<sub>2</sub></para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp15091008">
<para id="fs-idp15091264">(a) [Ag<sup>+</sup>] = [I<sup>–</sup>] = 1,3 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–5</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>; (b) [Ag<sup>+</sup>] = 2,88 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–2</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>SO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>= 1,44 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–2</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>; (c) [Mn<sup>2+</sup>] = 3,7 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–5</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>, [OH<sup>–</sup>] = 7,4 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–5</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>; (d) [Sr<sup>2+</sup>] = 4,3 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–2</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>, [OH<sup>–</sup>] = 8,6 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–2</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>; (e) [Mg<sup>2+</sup>] = 1,3 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–4</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>, [OH<sup>–</sup>] = 2,6 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–4</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>.</para></solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp1289872">
<problem id="fs-idp1290000">
<para id="fs-idp1290128">Eftirfarandi styrkur finnst í efnablöndum jóna í jafnvægi við torleyst föst efni. Út frá gefnum styrk, reiknaðu <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> fyrir hvert tilgreint torleyst fast efni:</para>
<para id="fs-idp1291616">(a) AgBr: [Ag<sup>+</sup>] = 5,7 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–7</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>, [Br<sup>–</sup>] = 5,7 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–7</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para>
<para id="fs-idp1295680">(b) CaCO<sub>3</sub>: [Ca<sup>2+</sup>] = 5,3 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> = 9,0 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–7</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para>
<para id="fs-idp1302560">(c) PbF<sub>2</sub>: [Pb<sup>2+</sup>] = 2,1 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>, [F<sup>–</sup>] = 4,2 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para>
<para id="fs-idp1307008">(d) Ag<sub>2</sub>CrO<sub>4</sub>: [Ag<sup>+</sup>] = 5,3 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–5</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>, 3,2 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para>
<para id="fs-idp1311456">(e) InF<sub>3</sub>: [In<sup>3+</sup>] = 2,3 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>, [F<sup>–</sup>] = 7,0 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp1351072">
<problem id="fs-idp1351200">
<para id="fs-idp1351328">Eftirfarandi styrkur finnst í efnablöndum jóna í jafnvægi við torleyst föst efni. Út frá gefnum styrk, reiknaðu <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> fyrir hvert tilgreint torleyst fast efni:</para>
<para id="fs-idp1352816">(a) TlCl: [Tl<sup>+</sup>] = 1,21 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–2</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>, [Cl<sup>–</sup>] = 1,2 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–2</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para>
<para id="fs-idp1356880">(b) Ce(IO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>4</sub>: [Ce<sup>4+</sup>] = 1,8 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–4</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>IO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> = 2,6 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–13</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para>
<para id="fs-idp1363984">(c) Gd<sub>2</sub>(SO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>3</sub>: [Gd<sup>3+</sup>] = 0,132 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>SO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>4</m:mtext></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> = 0,198 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para>
<para id="fs-idp1369344">(d) Ag<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>4</sub>: [Ag<sup>+</sup>] = 2,40 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–2</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>SO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>4</m:mtext></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> = 2,05 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–2</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para>
<para id="fs-idp1376112">(e) BaSO<sub>4</sub>: [Ba<sup>2+</sup>] = 0,500 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>SO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>4</m:mtext></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> = 2,16 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−10</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp1381728">
<para id="fs-idp1381984">(a) 1,45 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–4</sup>; (b) 8,2 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–55</sup>; (c) 1,35 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–4</sup>; (d) 1,18 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–5</sup>; (e) 1,08 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–10</sup></para></solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp1405168">
<problem id="fs-idp1405296">
<para id="fs-idp1405424">Hvort eftirfarandi efnasambanda fellur út úr lausn sem hefur tilgreindan styrk? (Sjá <link document="m68868">Appendix J</link> fyrir <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> gildi.)</para>
<para id="fs-idp1407680">(a) KClO<sub>4</sub>: [K<sup>+</sup>] = 0,01 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>ClO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> = 0,01 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para>
<para id="fs-idp1412608">(b) K<sub>2</sub>PtCl<sub>6</sub>: [K<sup>+</sup>] = 0,01 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>PtCl</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>6</m:mtext></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> = 0,01 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para>
<para id="fs-idp1417584">(c) PbI<sub>2</sub>: [Pb<sup>2+</sup>] = 0,003 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>, [I<sup>–</sup>] = 1,3 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para>
<para id="fs-idp1421136">(d) Ag<sub>2</sub>S: [Ag<sup>+</sup>] = 1 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–10</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>, [S<sup>2–</sup>] = 1 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–13</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp1466960">
<problem id="fs-idp1467088">
<para id="fs-idp1467216">Hvort eftirfarandi efnasambanda fellur út úr lausn sem hefur tilgreindan styrk? (Sjá <link document="m68868">Appendix J</link> fyrir <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> gildi.)</para>
<para id="fs-idp1469472">(a) CaCO<sub>3</sub>: [Ca<sup>2+</sup>] = 0,003 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>3</m:mtext></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> = 0,003 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para>
<para id="fs-idp1474064">(b) Co(OH)<sub>2</sub>: [Co<sup>2+</sup>] = 0,01 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>, [OH<sup>–</sup>] = 1 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–7</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para>
<para id="fs-idp1477616">(c) CaHPO<sub>4</sub>: [Ca<sup>2+</sup>] = 0,01 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HPO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>4</m:mtext></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> = 2 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–6</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para>
<para id="fs-idp1483104">(d) Pb<sub>3</sub>(PO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub>: [Pb<sup>2+</sup>] = 0,01 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>PO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>4</m:mtext></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>3−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>= 1 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–13</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp1489488">
<para id="fs-idp1489744">(a) CaCO<sub>3</sub> fellur út. (b) Efnasambandið fellur ekki út. (c) Efnasambandið fellur ekki út. (d) Efnasambandið fellur út.</para></solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp1563760">
<problem id="fs-idp1563888">
<para id="fs-idp1564016">Reiknaðu styrk Tl<sup>+</sup> þegar TlCl byrjar rétt að falla út úr lausn sem er 0,0250 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> í Cl<sup>–</sup>.</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp1572240">
<problem id="fs-idp1572368">
<para id="fs-idp1572496">Reiknaðu styrk súlfatjónar þegar BaSO<sub>4</sub> byrjar rétt að falla út úr lausn sem er 0,0758 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> í Ba<sup>2+</sup>.</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp1574464">
<para id="fs-idp1574720">1,42 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−9</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para></solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp1597744">
<problem id="fs-idp1597872">
<para id="fs-idp1598000">Reiknaðu styrk Sr<sup>2+</sup> þegar SrCrO<sub>4</sub> byrjar að falla út úr lausn sem er 0,0025 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> í CrO<sub>4</sub><sup>2–</sup>.</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp1626656">
<problem id="fs-idp1626784">
<para id="fs-idp1626912">Reiknaðu styrk <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>PO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>3−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> þegar Ag<sub>3</sub>PO<sub>4</sub> byrjar að falla út úr lausn sem er 0,0125 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> í Ag<sup>+</sup>.</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp1631136">
<para id="fs-idp1631392">9,2 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−13</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp1664496">
<problem id="fs-idp1664624">
<para id="fs-idp1664752">Reiknaðu styrk F<sup>–</sup> sem þarf til að útfelling CaF<sub>2</sub> hefjist í lausn sem er 0,010 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> í Ca<sup>2+</sup>.</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp1683696">
<problem id="fs-idp1683824">
<para id="fs-idp1683952">Reiknaðu styrk Ag<sup>+</sup> sem þarf til að útfelling Ag<sub>2</sub>CO<sub>3</sub> hefjist í lausn sem er 2,50 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–6</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> í <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp1689232">
<para id="fs-idp1689488">[Ag<sup>+</sup>] = 1,8 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–3</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp1720944">
<problem id="fs-idp1721072">
<para id="fs-idp1721200">Hvaða [Ag<sup>+</sup>] þarf til að minnka <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> niður í 8,2 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–4</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> með útfellingu Ag<sub>2</sub>CO<sub>3</sub>?</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp1744880">
<problem id="fs-idp1745008">
<para id="fs-idp1745136">Hvaða [F<sup>–</sup>] þarf til að minnka [Ca<sup>2+</sup>] niður í 1,0 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–4</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> með útfellingu CaF<sub>2</sub>?</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp1748416">
<para id="fs-idp1748672">6,3 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–4</sup></para></solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp1768416">
<problem id="fs-idp1768544">
<para id="fs-idp1768672">Rúmmáli 0,800 L af 2 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–4</sup>-<emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> Ba(NO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub> lausn er bætt við 0,200 L af 5 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–4</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> Li<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>4</sub>. Fellur BaSO<sub>4</sub> út? Útskýrðu svarið.</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp1809552">
<problem id="fs-idp1809680">
<para id="fs-idp1809808">Framkvæmdu þessa útreikninga fyrir nikkel(II)karbónat. (a) Með hvaða rúmmáli af vatni þarf að þvo botnfall sem inniheldur NiCO<sub>3</sub> til að leysa upp 0,100 g af þessu efnasambandi? Gerðu ráð fyrir að þvottavatnið verði mettað af NiCO<sub>3</sub> (<emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> = 1,36 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–7</sup>).</para>
<para id="fs-idp1812848">(b) Ef NiCO<sub>3</sub> væri óhreinindi í sýni af CoCO<sub>3</sub> (<emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> = 1,0 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–12</sup>), hvaða massi af CoCO<sub>3</sub> hefði tapast? Hafðu í huga að bæði NiCO<sub>3</sub> og CoCO<sub>3</sub> leysast upp í sömu lausninni.</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp1817248">
<para id="fs-idp1817504">(a) 2,25 L; (b) 7,2 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–7</sup> g</para></solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp1852800">
<problem id="fs-idp1852928">
<para id="fs-idp1853056">Járnstyrkur yfir 5,4 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–6</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> í vatni sem notað er í þvott getur valdið blettum. Hvaða [OH<sup>–</sup>] þarf til að minnka [Fe<sup>2+</sup>] niður í þetta magn með útfellingu Fe(OH)<sub>2</sub>?</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp1866352">
<problem id="fs-idp1866480">
<para id="fs-idp1866608">Lausn er 0,010 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> í bæði Cu<sup>2+</sup> og Cd<sup>2+</sup>. Hvaða hlutfall af Cd<sup>2+</sup> er eftir í lausninni þegar 99,9% af Cu<sup>2+</sup> hefur verið fellt út sem CuS með því að bæta við súlfíði?</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp1869472">
<para id="fs-idp1869728">100% af því er uppleyst</para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp1891472">
<problem id="fs-idp1891600">
<para id="fs-idp1891728">Lausn er 0,15 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> í bæði Pb<sup>2+</sup> og Ag<sup>+</sup>. Ef Cl<sup>–</sup> er bætt við þessa lausn, hvað er [Ag<sup>+</sup>] þegar PbCl<sub>2</sub> byrjar að falla út?</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp1955712">
<problem id="fs-idp1955840">
<para id="fs-idp1955968">Hvaða hvarfefni mætti nota til að aðskilja jónirnar í eftirfarandi efnablöndum, sem eru 0,1 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> með tilliti til hverrar jónar? Í sumum tilfellum gæti verið nauðsynlegt að stjórna pH. (Vísbending: Skoðaðu <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> gildin í <link document="m68868">Appendix J</link>.)</para>
<para id="fs-idp1958976">(a) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Hg</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> og Cu<sup>2+</sup></para>
<para id="fs-idp1961408">(b) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>SO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> og Cl<sup>–</sup></para>
<para id="fs-idp1963872">(c) Hg<sup>2+</sup> og Co<sup>2+</sup></para>
<para id="fs-idp1964896">(d) Zn<sup>2+</sup> og Sr<sup>2+</sup></para>
<para id="fs-idp1965920">(e) Ba<sup>2+</sup> og Mg<sup>2+</sup></para>
<para id="fs-idp1966944">(f) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> og OH<sup>–</sup></para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp1969536">
<para id="fs-idp1969792">(a) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Hg</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> og Cu<sup>2+</sup>: Bætið við <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>SO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> (b) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>SO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> og Cl<sup>–</sup>: Bætið við Ba<sup>2+</sup>. (c) Hg<sup>2+</sup> og Co<sup>2+</sup>: Bætið við S<sup>2–</sup>. (d) Zn<sup>2+</sup> og Sr<sup>2+</sup>: Bætið við OH<sup>–</sup> þar til [OH<sup>–</sup>] = 0,050 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>. (e) Ba<sup>2+</sup> og Mg<sup>2+</sup>: Bætið við <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>SO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> (f) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> og OH<sup>–</sup>: Bætið við Ba<sup>2+</sup>.</para></solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp2172896">
<problem id="fs-idp2173024">
<para id="fs-idp2173152">Lausn inniheldur 1,0 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–5</sup> mól af KBr og 0,10 mól af KCl á hvern lítra. AgNO<sub>3</sub> er smám saman bætt út í þessa lausn. Hvað myndast fyrst, fast AgBr eða fast AgCl?</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp2204496">
<problem id="fs-idp2204624">
<para id="fs-idp2204752">Lausn inniheldur 1,0 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–2</sup> mól af KI og 0,10 mól af KCl á hvern lítra. AgNO<sub>3</sub> er smám saman bætt út í þessa lausn. Hvað myndast fyrst, fast AgI eða fast AgCl?</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp2206656">
<para id="fs-idp2206912">AgI fellur fyrst út.</para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp2236432">
<problem id="fs-idp2236560">
<para id="fs-idp2236688">Kalsíumjónir í blóðvatni manna eru nauðsynlegar fyrir storknun (<link target-id="CNX_Chem_15_01_Blood"/>). Kalíumoxalat, K<sub>2</sub>C<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub>, er notað sem segavarnarlyf þegar blóðsýni er tekið fyrir rannsóknarstofupróf því það fjarlægir kalsíum sem botnfall af CaC<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub>·H<sub>2</sub>O. Nauðsynlegt er að fjarlægja allt nema 1,0% af Ca<sup>2+</sup> í blóðvatni til að koma í veg fyrir storknun. Ef venjulegt blóðvatn með stuðpúðastýrðu pH-gildi 7,40 inniheldur 9,5 mg af Ca<sup>2+</sup> í hverjum 100 ml af blóðvatni, hvaða massa af K<sub>2</sub>C<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub> þarf til að koma í veg fyrir storknun 10 ml blóðsýnis sem er 55% blóðvatn miðað við rúmmál? (Öll rúmmál eru nákvæm með tveimur markverðum stöfum. Athugið að rúmmál blóðvatns í 10 ml blóðsýni er 5,5 ml. Gerum ráð fyrir að <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> gildi fyrir CaC<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub> í blóðvatni sé það sama og í vatni.)</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp2313504">
<problem id="fs-idp2313632">
<para id="fs-idp2313760">Um 50% af þvagsteinum (nýrnasteinum) samanstanda af kalsíumfosfati, Ca<sub>3</sub>(PO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub>. Venjulegt meðalmagn kalsíums sem skilst út með þvagi er 0,10 g af Ca<sup>2+</sup> á dag. Gera má ráð fyrir að venjulegt meðalmagn þvags sem skilst út sé 1,4 L á dag. Hver er hámarksstyrkur fosfatjónar sem þvag getur innihaldið áður en steinn byrjar að myndast?</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp2316016">
<para id="fs-idp2316272">1,5 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−12</sup> <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis></para></solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp2372080">
<problem id="fs-idp2372208">
<para id="fs-idp2372336">pH venjulegs þvags er 6,30 og heildarstyrkur fosfats <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:mtext>PO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>3−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> + <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>HPO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> + <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>PO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> + [H<sub>3</sub>PO<sub>4</sub>]) er 0,020 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>. Hver er lágmarksstyrkur Ca<sup>2+</sup> sem er nauðsynlegur til að koma af stað myndun nýrnasteina? (Sjá <link target-id="fs-idp2313504"/> fyrir frekari upplýsingar.)</para></problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp2651392">
<problem id="fs-idp2651520">
<para id="fs-idp2651648">Magnesíummálmur (hluti af melmum sem notaðir eru í flugvélar og afoxunarefni sem notað er við framleiðslu úrans, títans og annarra virkra málma) er einangraður úr sjó með eftirfarandi röð efnahvarfa:</para>
<para id="fs-idp262554736"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Mg</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ca(OH)</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⟶</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Mg(OH)</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Ca</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp276697552"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Mg(OH)</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mtext>2HCl(</m:mtext><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo stretchy="false">⟶</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>MgCl</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>2H</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>l</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp60740640"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>MgCl</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>l</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mover><m:mo>→</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mspace width="0.7em"/><m:mtext>electrolysis</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.7em"/></m:mrow></m:mover><m:mtext>Mg</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Cl</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>g</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp2681472">Sjór hefur eðlismassa 1,026 g/cm<sup>3</sup> og inniheldur 1272 hluta af milljón af magnesíum sem Mg<sup>2+</sup>(<emphasis effect="italics">aq</emphasis>) miðað við massa. Hvaða massa, í kílógrömmum, af Ca(OH)<sub>2</sub> þarf til að fella út 99,9% af magnesíum í 1,00 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>3</sup> L af sjó?</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp2684864">
<para id="fs-idp2685120">3,99 kg</para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp2754176">
<problem id="fs-idp2754304">
<para id="fs-idp2754432">Brennisteinsvetni er leitt í gegnum lausn sem er 0,10 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> bæði í Pb<sup>2+</sup> og Fe<sup>2+</sup> og 0,30 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> í HCl. Eftir að lausnin hefur náð jafnvægi er hún mettuð af H<sub>2</sub>S ([H<sub>2</sub>S] = 0,10 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis>). Hvaða styrkur Pb<sup>2+</sup> og Fe<sup>2+</sup> er eftir í lausninni? Fyrir mettaða lausn af H<sub>2</sub>S getum við notað jafnvægið:</para>
<equation id="fs-idp2759536" class="unnumbered"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>S</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>2H</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>l</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>2H</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mtext>S</m:mtext><m:mtext>2−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>q</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mspace width="4em"/><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.0</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:msup><m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>26</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></equation>
<para id="fs-idp2774352">(Vísbending: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mtext>+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> breytist þegar málmsúlfíð falla út.)</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp2814128">
<problem id="fs-idp2814256">
<para id="fs-idp2814384">Framkvæmdu eftirfarandi útreikninga sem varða styrk joðatjóna:</para>
<para id="fs-idp2814768">(a) Styrkur joðatjónar í mettaðri lausn af La(IO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>3</sub> reyndist vera 3,1 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–3</sup> mól/L. Finndu <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub>.</para>
<para id="fs-idp2817760">(b) Finndu styrk joðatjóna í mettaðri lausn af Cu(IO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub> (<emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> = 7,4 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–8</sup>).</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp2820816">
<para id="fs-idp2821072">(a) 3,1 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–11</sup>; (b) [Cu<sup>2+</sup>] = 2,6 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–3</sup>; <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>IO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> = 5,3 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–3</sup></para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp2852912">
<problem id="fs-idp2853040">
<para id="fs-idp2853168">Reiknaðu mólarleysni AgBr í 0,035 <emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> NaBr (<emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> = 5 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–13</sup>).</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp2865680">
<problem id="fs-idp2865808">
<para id="fs-idp2865936">Hversu mörg grömm af Pb(OH)<sub>2</sub> leysast upp í 500 ml af 0,050-<emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> PbCl<sub>2</sub> lausn (<emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> = 1,2 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–15</sup>)?</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp2869712">
<para id="fs-idp2869968">9,3 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–6</sup> g Pb(OH)<sub>2</sub></para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp2894848">
<problem id="fs-idp2894976">
<para id="fs-idp2895104">Notaðu <link url="http://openstax.org/l/16solublesalts">herminn</link> úr fyrri hlekknum til að ljúka við eftirfarandi verkefni. Notaðu 0,01 g af CaF<sub>2</sub> og gefðu upp K<sub>sp</sub> gildin sem finnast í 0,2-<emphasis effect="italics">M</emphasis> lausn af hverju salti. Ræddu hvers vegna gildin breytast þegar þú skiptir um auðleyst sölt.</para></problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp2904912">
<problem id="fs-idp2905040">
<para id="fs-idp2905168">Hversu mörg grömm af magnesíummjólk, Mg(OH)<sub>2</sub> (<emphasis effect="italics">s</emphasis>) (58,3 g/mól), væru leysanleg í 200 ml af vatni. <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> = 7,1 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–12</sup>. Láttu jónahvarfið og jöfnuna fyrir <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> fylgja með í svarinu þínu. (<emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>w</sub> = 1 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–14</sup> = [H<sub>3</sub>O<sup>+</sup>][OH<sup>–</sup>])</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp2913408">
<para id="fs-idp2913664"><m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>Mg(OH)</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">(</m:mo><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">)</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">⇌</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Mg</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>2OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mspace width="4em"/><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>Mg</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>2+</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mtext>OH</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext></m:msup><m:mo stretchy="false">]</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math><newline/> 1,23 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>−3</sup> g Mg(OH)<sub>2</sub></para></solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp2945408">
<problem id="fs-idp2945536">
<para id="fs-idp2945664">Tvö tilgátusölt, LM<sub>2</sub> og LQ, hafa sama mólarleysni í H<sub>2</sub>O. Ef <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> fyrir LM<sub>2</sub> er 3,20 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–5</sup>, hvert er þá <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> gildið fyrir LQ?</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp2976256">
<problem id="fs-idp2976384">
<para id="fs-idp2976512">Styrkur karbónatjónarinnar er aukinn smám saman í lausn sem inniheldur jafnan styrk af tvígildum katjónum magnesíums, kalsíums, strontíums, baríums og mangans. Hvert af eftirfarandi karbónötum fellur út fyrst? Hvert fellur út síðast? Útskýrðu.</para>
<para id="fs-idp2977392">(a) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>MgCO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub>
<m:mo>•</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:msub><m:mtext>H</m:mtext><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mtext>O</m:mtext><m:mspace width="4em"/><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:msup><m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp2982720">(b) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>CaCO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mspace width="4em"/><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8.7</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:msup><m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp2988048">(c) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>SrCO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mspace width="4em"/><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:msup><m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp2993376">(d) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>BaCO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mspace width="4em"/><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.6</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:msup><m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp2998704">(e) <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mrow><m:mtext>MnCO</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msub><m:mspace width="4em"/><m:msub><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>sp</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8.8</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:msup><m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>11</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math></para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp3004160">
<para id="fs-idp3004416">MnCO<sub>3</sub> mun myndast fyrst þar sem það hefur lægsta <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> gildið meðal þessara samsvarandi efnasambanda og er því minnst leysanlegt. MgCO<sub>3</sub>•3H<sub>2</sub>O fellur út síðast þar sem það hefur hæsta K_sp gildið og er mest leysanlegt. <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> gildi.</para></solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp3007504">
<problem id="fs-idp3007632">
<para id="fs-idp3007760">Hversu mörg grömm af Zn(CN)<sub>2</sub>(<emphasis effect="italics">s</emphasis>) (117,44 g/mól) væru leysanleg í 100 ml af H<sub>2</sub>O? Láttu stillt efnahvarf og jöfnuna fyrir <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> fylgja með í svarinu þínu. <emphasis effect="italics">K</emphasis><sub>sp</sub> gildið fyrir Zn(CN)<sub>2</sub>(<emphasis effect="italics">s</emphasis>) er 3,0 <m:math><m:mo>×</m:mo></m:math> 10<sup>–16</sup>.</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
</section>
</content>
<glossary>
<definition id="fs-idp3050576">
<term>samjónahrif (e. common ion effect)</term>
<meaning id="fs-idp3050576-meaning">áhrif á jafnvægi þegar efni með jón sem er sameiginleg með uppleystu efnategundinni er bætt við lausnina; veldur minnkun á leysni jónaefnis, eða minnkun á jónun veikar sýru eða basa</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idp3051616">
<term>mólarleysni (e. molar solubility)</term>
<meaning id="fs-idp3051616-meaning">leysni efnasambands gefið upp í einingunni mól á lítra (mól/L)</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idp3052416">
<term>valbundin útfelling (e. selective precipitation)</term>
<meaning id="fs-idp3052416-meaning">ferli þar sem jónir eru aðskildar með því að nýta mismunandi leysni þeirra með tilteknu útfellingarhvarfefni</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idp3053344">
<term>leysnimargfeldisfasti (Ksp) (e. solubility product constant (ksp))</term>
<meaning id="fs-idp3053344-meaning">jafnvægisfasti fyrir upplausn jónaefnis</meaning>
</definition>
</glossary>
</document>